le.'=>'無法產生型錄檔案。','Finish checkout'=>'完成結帳','. Authorization ID: %1$s not found. Please log into your %2$sPayPal account%3$s to capture the payment'=>'。 找不到授權 ID %1$s。 請登入你的 %2$sPayPal 帳號%3$s擷取付款資訊','<strong>Sandbox mode enabled</strong>. Only sandbox test accounts can be used. See the <a href="%s">PayPal Sandbox Testing Guide</a> for more details.'=>'<strong>沙盒模式已啟用</strong>。 只能使用沙盒測試帳號。 如需詳細資料，請參閱 <a href="%s">PayPal 沙盒測試指引</a>。','Your PayPal account has been restricted by PayPal. This may prevent customers from completing payments. Please %1$scontact PayPal support%2$s to resolve this issue and restore full functionality to your account.'=>'PayPal 已限制你的帳號。 這可能造成顧客無法完成付款。 請%1$s聯絡 PayPal 支援團隊%2$s解決此問題，為你的帳號還原完整功能。','PayPal Account Restricted'=>'PayPal 帳號已受限','PayPal Standard does not support your store currency (%s).'=>'PayPal 標準版不支援你商店的貨幣 (%s)。','Notifies customers when their order has been partially or fully refunded.'=>'通知客戶其訂單已部分或全額退款。','Account password reset'=>'帳號密碼重設','Notifies customers when their password has been reset.'=>'重設客戶的密碼時通知客戶。','Notifies admins when an order that was processing or on hold has failed.'=>'處理中或保留的訂單失敗時通知管理員。','Notifies admins when a new order has been placed.'=>'在下訂新訂單時通知管理員。','Order changes'=>'訂單變更','Preheader'=>'前標題','Shown as a preview in the Inbox, next to the subject line. (Max 150 characters).'=>'在收件匣中，在主旨行旁顯示為預覽。 (上限為 150 個字元)。','Notifies customers when you’ve added a note to their order.'=>'在將備註新增至訂單時通知客戶。','Order on hold'=>'訂單保留中','Notifies customers when their order has been placed on hold.'=>'在客戶的訂單保留時通知客戶。','POS order complete'=>'POS 訂單已完成','Notifies customers when their in-person (POS) order has been completed.'=>'當客戶親自下單 (POS) 完成時通知客戶。','POS order refunded'=>'POS訂單已退款','Notifies customers when a full or partial refund has been issued for their in-person (POS) order.'=>'為客戶親自下單 (POS) 發放全額或部份退款時，通知客戶。','Notifies customers when their order has been received and is being processed.'=>'收到客戶訂單且正在處理中時通知客戶。','Notifies customers when their order has failed.'=>'在客戶訂單失敗時通知客戶。','Payment request'=>'請款','Manually send customers an email to review their order and complete payment.'=>'手動傳送電子郵件給客戶，以檢閱其訂單並完成付款。','Account created'=>'帳號已建立','Notifies customers when their account has been created.'=>'建立客戶帳號時通知客戶。','Customer note added'=>'已新增客戶備註','You do not have permission to save settings.'=>'你無權限儲存設定。','Add a different email address to receive replies.'=>'新增不同的電子郵件地址以接收回覆。','Please choose product options for %1$s.'=>'請選擇 %1$s 的商品選項。','Payment via %1$s (%2$s).'=>'透過 %1$s 付款 (%2$s)。','Payment complete.'=>'付款已完成。','Canceled order'=>'取消的訂單','Notifies admins when an order that was processing or on hold has been canceled.'=>'當正在處理或保留的訂單取消時通知管理員。','Notifies customers when their order has been cancelled.'=>'在客戶訂單取消時通知客戶。','Order fulfilled'=>'訂單已履行','Notifies customers when their order has been shipped.'=>'在客戶訂單出貨時通知客戶。','REST API operations for WooCommerce resources including products, orders, and other store data.'=>'WooCommerce 資源的 REST API 作業，包括商品、訂單和其他商店資料。','block descriptionDisplays the description of the selected variation.'=>'顯示所選款式的說明。','block titleVariation Description (Beta)'=>'款式說明 (測試版)','This item is not available for purchase.'=>'你無法購買此項目。','Raw shipping method settings for frontend processing.'=>'前端處理的原始運送方式設定。','Shipping method ID (e.g., flat_rate, free_shipping).'=>'運送方式 ID (例如 flat_rate、free_shipping)。','Whether the shipping method is enabled.'=>'是否啟用運送方式。','Shipping methods for this zone.'=>'此區域的運送方式。','Unique identifier for the shipping zone.'=>'運送區域唯一識別碼。','Invalid line items type.'=>'細項類型無效。','The fulfillment status of the order.'=>'訂單的履行狀態。','A list of line items (products) within this order.'=>'此訂單中的細項 (商品) 清單。','Product needs shipping.'=>'商品需要運送。','Product is downloadable.'=>'商品是可下載的產品。','Product is virtual.'=>'商品是虛擬產品。','Product global unique ID.'=>'商品全域唯一 ID。','Product permalink.'=>'商品永久連結。','Item price. Calculated as total / quantity.'=>'項目價格。 以總計 / 數量計算。','Product data this item is linked to.'=>'此項目連結的商品資料。','Product or variation ID.'=>'商品或款式 ID。','Line item image, if available.'=>'細項圖片 (如果有的話)。','Item name.'=>'項目名稱。','Limit result set to orders with specific fulfillment statuses.'=>'將結果集限制為具有特定履行狀態的訂單。','Total value must be an array with exactly 2 numbers for between operators.'=>'總計值必須是一組數字，且陣列中的 between 運算子正好是 2 個數字。','The comparison operator to use for total filtering.'=>'用於總計篩選的比較運算子。','Limit result set to orders with specific total amounts. For between operators, list two values.'=>'將結果集限制在具有特定總金額的訂單。 對於 between 運算子，請列出兩個值。','If true, the note will be shown to customers. If false, the note will be for admin reference only.'=>'如果為 true，將會向顧客顯示備註。 如果為 false，備註將僅供管理員參考。','Order ID the note belongs to.'=>'備註所屬的訂單 ID。','The order ID that notes belong to.'=>'備註所屬的訂單 ID。','Limit result to customer notes or private notes.'=>'將結果限制為顧客備註或私人備註。','Trash not supported.'=>'不支援垃圾桶。','Cannot trash resource.'=>'無法回收資源。','Cannot delete resource.'=>'無法刪除資源。','Cannot create resource.'=>'無法建立資源。','Resource already exists.'=>'資源已存在。','Invalid error object provided.'=>'提供的錯誤物件無效。','An error occurred while processing your request.'=>'處理要求時發生錯誤。','The user associated with this API key no longer exists.'=>'與此 API 金鑰關聯的使用者不再存在。','Authentication failed.'=>'驗證失敗。','X-MCP-API-Key must be in format consumer_key:consumer_secret'=>'X-MCP-API-Key 的格式必須為 consumer_key:consumer_secret','X-MCP-API-Key header required. Format: consumer_key:consumer_secret'=>'需要 X-MCP-API-Key 標頭。 格式：consumer_key:consumer_secret','HTTPS is required for MCP requests.'=>'MCP 要求需要 HTTPS。','AI-accessible WooCommerce operations via MCP'=>'透過 MCP 實現 AI 可存取的 WooCommerce 作業','WooCommerce MCP Server'=>'WooCommerce MCP 伺服器','Ambiguous shipping providers list.'=>'模糊的運送供應商清單。','Configure Permalinks'=>'設定永久連結','WordPress permalinks must be set to anything other than "Plain" for MCP to work.'=>'必須將 WordPress 永久連結設為「一般」以外的任何值，MCP 才能運作。','Configuration Required'=>'需要設定','Enable WooCommerce MCP (Model Context Protocol) for AI-powered store operations. AI-generated results and actions can be unpredictable - please review before executing in your store.'=>'啟用 WooCommerce MCP (模型內容通訊協定) 以進行 AI 支援的商店作業。 無法預測 AI 產生的結果和動作：請在商店中執行前先檢閱。','[Performance] Removes session cookies for non-logged in customers when session data is empty, improving page caching performance. May cause compatibility issues with extensions that depend on the session cookie without using session data.'=>'[效能] 在工作階段資料為空白時，移除未登入顧客的工作階段 Cookie，以改善頁面快取效能。 可能會造成與工作階段 Cookie 相依且未使用工作階段資料的擴充功能發生相容性問題。','Clear Customer Sessions When Empty'=>'空白時清除顧客工作階段','Sample Download File.pdf'=>'下載 File.pdf 範例','Dummy Downloadable Product'=>'可下載的示範商品','Unique identifier for the resource'=>'資源的唯一識別碼','Update an existing order by modifying status, customer information, line items, or other order details.'=>'修改狀態、顧客資訊、細項或其他訂單詳細資料，以更新現有訂單。','Update Order'=>'更新訂單','Create a new order with customer information, line items, shipping details, and payment information.'=>'建立包含顧客資訊、細項、運送詳細資料和付款資訊的新訂單。','Create Order'=>'建立訂單','Retrieve detailed information about a single order by ID, including line items, customer details, and payment information.'=>'依 ID 擷取單一訂單的詳細資訊，包括細項、顧客詳細資料和付款資訊。','Get Order'=>'取得訂單','Retrieve a paginated list of orders with optional filters for status, customer, date range, and other criteria.'=>'擷取訂單的分頁清單，其中包含狀態、顧客、日期範圍與其他條件的選用篩選條件。','List Orders'=>'列出訂單','Permanently delete a product from the store. This action cannot be undone.'=>'將商品從商店中永久刪除。 此動作無法復原。','Delete Product'=>'刪除商品','Update an existing product by modifying its attributes such as price, stock, description, or metadata.'=>'修改現有商品的屬性 (例如價格、庫存、說明或中繼資料)，以進行更新。','Update Product'=>'更新商品','Create a new product in WooCommerce with name, price, description, and other product attributes.'=>'在 WooCommerce 中建立具有名稱、價格、說明和其他商品屬性的新商品。','Retrieve detailed information about a single product by ID, including price, description, images, and metadata.'=>'依 ID 擷取單一商品的詳細資訊，包括價格、說明、圖片和中繼資料。','Get Product'=>'取得商品','Retrieve a paginated list of products with optional filters for status, category, price range, and other attributes.'=>'擷取商品分頁清單，其中包含狀態、分類、價格範圍和其他屬性的選用篩選條件。','List Products'=>'商品上架','Please select a valid quantity to add to the cart.'=>'請選取要新增至購物車的有效數量。','Play'=>'播放','Watch on YouTube'=>'在 YouTube 觀看','Listen on ReverbNation'=>'在 ReverbNation 收聽','Listen on Mixcloud'=>'在 Mixcloud 收聽','Listen on Pocket Casts'=>'在 Pocket Casts 收聽','Listen on SoundCloud'=>'在 SoundCloud 收聽','Listen on Spotify'=>'在 Spotify 收聽','Listen to the audio'=>'收聽音訊','Description for the setting field.'=>'設定欄位的說明。','Available options for select/multiselect fields.'=>'選取/多選欄位的可用選項。','Set your store\'s address, visibility, currency, language, and timezone.'=>'設定商店的地址、可見度、貨幣、語言和時區。','Flat key-value mapping of all setting field values.'=>'所有設定欄位值的固定鍵值對應。','Invalid country code in list.'=>'清單中的國家/地區代碼無效。','Expected an array of country codes.'=>'預期是一組國家/地區代碼。','Invalid shipping location option.'=>'運送地點選項無效。','Invalid selling location option.'=>'銷售地點選項無效。','Invalid country/state format.'=>'國家/地區或州/省格式無效。','Number of decimals must be between 0 and 10.'=>'小數位數必須介於 0 到 10 之間。','Setting field value.'=>'設定欄位值。','Setting field description.'=>'設定欄位描述。','Setting field type.'=>'設定欄位類型。','Setting field label.'=>'設定欄位標籤。','Setting field ID.'=>'設定欄位 ID。','Settings fields.'=>'設定欄位。','Display order for the group.'=>'顯示群組的順序。','Group description.'=>'群組說明。','Group title.'=>'群組標題。','Settings group.'=>'設定群組。','Collection of setting groups.'=>'設定群組集合。','Settings description.'=>'設定說明。','Settings title.'=>'設定標題。','Unique identifier for the settings group.'=>'設定群組的單一識別碼。','Customize the look and feel of all you notification emails.'=>'自訂所有通知電子郵件的外觀和風格。','Email design'=>'電子郵件設計','Add "Reply-to" email'=>'新增「回覆」電子郵件','Please enter a valid reply-to email address.'=>'請輸入有效的回覆電子郵件地址。','Reply-to name cannot be empty when reply-to is enabled.'=>'啟用回覆功能時，回覆名稱不可為空白。','Reply-to enabled must be a boolean value.'=>'啟用的回覆功能必須是布林值。','Email sender name cannot be empty.'=>'電子郵件寄件者名稱不可為空白。','Invalid or empty request body.'=>'要求本文無效或為空白。','Add to cart single text.'=>'新增至購物車單一文字。','Add to cart text.'=>'新增至購物車文字。','Add to cart description.'=>'新增至購物車說明。','Add to cart details.'=>'新增至購物車詳細資料。','Sorry, you cannot update resources.'=>'抱歉，你無法更新資源。','The entity type must be "order".'=>'實體類型必須是「訂單」。','The entity ID is required.'=>'實體 ID 為必填項目。','The order ID is required.'=>'訂單 ID 為必填項目。','Sorry, you are not allowed to perform this action.'=>'抱歉，你無權執行此動作。','When enabled, PayPal will use the address provided by the checkout form, and prevent the buyer from changing it inside the PayPal payment page. Disable this to let buyers choose a shipping address from their PayPal account. PayPal verifies addresses therefore this setting can cause errors (we recommend keeping it disabled).'=>'啟用後，PayPal 會使用結帳表單提供的地址，而且會避免買家在 PayPal 付款頁面中變更地址。 停用此選項，讓買家從 PayPal 帳號選擇運送地址。 PayPal 會驗證地址，因此此設定可能會造成錯誤 (我們建議將其停用)。','Prevent buyers from changing the shipping address.'=>'避免買家變更運送地址。','Payment pending (reason: %s).'=>'待付款 (原因：%s)。','Enable PayPal buttons to offer PayPal, Venmo and Pay Later as express checkout options on product, cart, and checkout pages.'=>'啟用 PayPal 按鈕，在商品、購物車和結帳頁面提供 PayPal、Venmo 和「稍後付款」等快速結帳選項。','Enable PayPal Buttons'=>'啟用 PayPal 按鈕','PayPal Buttons'=>'PayPal 按鈕','PayPal payment authorized. Transaction ID: %1$s. Change payment status to processing or complete to capture funds.'=>'已授權 PayPal 付款。 交易 ID：%1$s。 將付款狀態變更為處理中或完成，以獲取款項。','PayPal payment captured. Transaction ID: %1$s.'=>'已獲取 PayPal 款項。 交易 ID：%1$s。','PayPal payment approval failed. PayPal Order ID: %1$s. Status: %2$s'=>'PayPal 付款核准失敗。 PayPal 訂單 ID：%1$s。 狀態：%2$s','PayPal payment approved. PayPal Order ID: %1$s'=>'PayPal 付款已核准。 PayPal 訂單 ID：%1$s','PayPal capture authorized payment failed'=>'PayPal 獲取授權款項失敗','. PayPal debug ID: %s'=>'。 PayPal 偵錯 ID：%s','PayPal %1$s payment failed. PayPal Order ID: %2$s'=>'PayPal %1$s 付款失敗。 PayPal 訂單 ID：%2$s','PayPal order creation failed. PayPal debug ID: %1$s'=>'PayPal 訂單建立失敗。 PayPal 偵錯 ID：%1$s','WooCommerce has upgraded your PayPal integration from PayPal Standard to PayPal Payments (PPCP), for a more reliable and modern checkout experience. If you do not prefer the upgraded integration in WooCommerce, we recommend switching to %1$sPayPal Payments%2$s extension.'=>'WooCommerce 已將 PayPal 整合功能從 PayPal 標準版升級為 PayPal 付款 (PPCP)，可實現更可靠且現代化的結帳體驗。 若你不想升級 WooCommerce 中的整合功能，建議切換至 %1$sPayPal 付款%2$s擴充功能。','An unknown error occurred'=>'發生不明錯誤','We are unable to process your PayPal payment at this time. Please try again or use a different payment method.'=>'我們目前無法處理 PayPal 付款。 請再試一次，或使用不同的付款方式。','Enable taxes and coupons and configure how they are calculated.'=>'啟用稅金與優惠券並設定其計算方式。','Taxes and coupons'=>'稅金和優惠券','Dādra and Nagar Haveli and Damān and Diu'=>'Dādra 和 Nagar Haveli 和 Damān 和 Diu','Requires a plugin with predictive address search support (e.g. <a href="%s" target="_blank">WooPayments</a>).'=>'需要具備可預測位址搜尋支援的外掛程式 (例如 <a href="%s" target="_blank">WooPayments</a>)。','block titleActive Filters'=>'使用中的篩選條件','block titleStatus Filter'=>'狀態篩選','block titleAttribute Filter'=>'屬性篩選條件','block titlePrice Filter'=>'價格篩選條件','block descriptionA placeholder block for email content.'=>'電子郵件內容的預留位置區塊。','block titleEmail Content'=>'電子郵件內容','Full screen image'=>'全螢幕圖片','Notify me'=>'通知我','back in stock formEnter your e-mail'=>'輸入電子郵件','back in stock formEmail address to be notified when this product is back in stock'=>'在此商品重新上架時要通知的電子郵件地址','Want to be notified when this product is back in stock?'=>'想要在此產品重新上架時收到通知嗎？','You have received this message because your e-mail address was used to sign up for stock notifications on our store. Wasn\'t you? Please get in touch with us if you keep receiving these messages.'=>'電子郵件地址已註冊本商店的庫存通知，因此你會收到此訊息。 不是你本人？ 如果你持續收到此類訊息，請與我們聯絡。','This link will remain active for %s.'=>'此連結會在 %s 前保持啟用。','To stop receiving these messages, %s to unsubscribe.'=>'若要停止收到此類訊息，%s以取消訂閱。','unsubscribe cta for stock notifications for guestsclick here'=>'按一下此處','To manage your notifications, %s to log in to your account.'=>'若要管理通知，%s以登入帳號。','unsubscribe cta for stock notifications for existing customersclick here'=>'按一下此處','You have received this message because your e-mail address was used to sign up for stock notifications on our store.'=>'電子郵件地址已註冊本商店的庫存通知，因此你會收到此訊息。','Back-in-stock notifications for this product are now being processed. Subscribed customers will receive these emails over the next few minutes. You can monitor or manage individual subscriptions on the <a href="%s">Stock Notifications page</a>.'=>'該商品的補貨通知現正處理中。 訂閱的顧客將在接下來的幾分鐘內收到這類電子郵件。 你可以在<a href="%s">庫存通知頁面</a>監控或管理個別訂閱。','Removed back-in-stock notification for product id: %d'=>'已移除以下商品 ID 的補貨通知：%d','WooCommerce Customer Stock Notifications'=>'WooCommerce 顧客庫存通知','User Email is invalid.'=>'使用者電子郵件無效。','User ID or User Email is required.'=>'必須輸入使用者 ID 或使用者電子郵件。','Product ID is required.'=>'商品 ID 為必填欄位。','notice actionManage notifications'=>'管理通知','notice actionResend verification'=>'重新傳送驗證','You have already joined this waitlist. Please complete the sign-up process by following the verification link sent to your e-mail.'=>'你已加入此等候清單。 請點選已傳送至電子郵件地址的驗證連結，以完成註冊程序。','You have already joined this waitlist.'=>'你已加入此等候清單。','Thanks for signing up! An account has been created for you. Please complete the sign-up process by following the verification link sent to your e-mail.'=>'感謝註冊！ 已為你建立帳號。 請點選已傳送至電子郵件地址的驗證連結，以完成註冊程序。','You have successfully signed up and will be notified when "%s" is back in stock! Note that a new account has been created for you; please check your e-mail for details.'=>'你已成功註冊，當「%s」重新上架時，你會收到通知！ 請注意，系統已為你建立新的帳號；請查看電子郵件以瞭解詳情。','Thanks for signing up! Please complete the sign-up process by following the verification link sent to your e-mail.'=>'感謝註冊！ 請點選已傳送至電子郵件地址的驗證連結，以完成註冊程序。','You have successfully signed up! You will be notified when "%s" is back in stock.'=>'你已成功註冊！ 當「%s」重新上架時，你會收到通知。','Failed to sign up. Please try again.'=>'註冊失敗。 請再試一次。','You have already signed up too many times. Please try again later.'=>'你已註冊過多次。 請稍後再試。','To proceed, please consent to the creation of a new account with your e-mail.'=>'若要繼續，請同意使用電子郵件地址建立新帳號。','Invalid email address.'=>'電子郵件地址無效。','Invalid user.'=>'使用者無效。','back in stock formhere'=>'這裡','You have already joined the waitlist! Click {manage_account_link} to manage your notifications.'=>'你已加入等候清單！ 按一下「{manage_account_link}」以管理通知。','back in stock formlog in'=>'登入','Please {login_link} to sign up for stock notifications.'=>'請{login_link}以註冊庫存通知。','Successfully unsubscribed %1$s. You will not receive a notification when "%2$s" becomes available.'=>'%1$s 已成功取消訂閱。 當「%2$s」可購買時，您將不會收到通知。','Successfully verified stock notifications for "%s".'=>'已成功驗證「%s」的庫存通知。','Stock Notification confirm notificationConfirm'=>'確認','Please follow the link below to complete the sign-up process and join the "{product_name}" waitlist.'=>'請點選以下連結完成註冊程序，即可加入「{product_name}」的等候清單。','Confirm sign-up'=>'確認註冊','Join the "{product_name}" waitlist.'=>'加入「{product_name}」的等候清單。','Verification e-mail sent to customers, as part of the double opt-in sign-up process.'=>'傳送給顧客的驗證電子郵件，這是雙重加入註冊程序的一部分。','Back in stock sign-up verification'=>'重新上架註冊驗證','Thanks for joining the waitlist! You will hear from us again when "{product_name}" is back in stock.'=>'感謝加入等候清單！ 當「{product_name}」重新上架時，我們會通知你。','Sign-up successful'=>'註冊成功','You have joined the "{product_name}" waitlist.'=>'你已加入「{product_name}」的等候清單。','Email sent to customers after completing the sign-up process successfully.'=>'成功完成註冊程序後傳送給顧客的電子郵件。','Back in stock sign-up confirmation'=>'重新上架註冊確認','Text to appear below the main e-mail header.'=>'顯示在主要電子郵件標頭下方的文字。','Email notificationShop Now'=>'立即選購','Great news: "{product_name}" is now available for purchase.'=>'好消息：「{product_name}」已可購買。','It\'s back in stock!'=>'本商品已重新上架！','"{product_