e this field empty if you would like to store expired sign-up requests indefinitey.'=>'控制外掛程式在資料庫中儲存未驗證通知註冊的時間長度。 如果你希望無限期儲存已過期的註冊要求，請輸入零或將此欄位保持空白。','Delete unverified notification sign-ups after (in days)'=>'在 (一定天數) 後刪除未驗證的通知註冊','To complete the sign-up process, customers must follow a verification link sent to their e-mail after submitting the sign-up form.'=>'若要完成註冊程序，顧客必須在提交註冊表單後，點選傳送至其電子郵件地址的驗證連結。','Require double opt-in to sign up'=>'需要雙重加入以註冊','Let customers sign up to be notified when products in your store are restocked.'=>'提供註冊選項，讓顧客在商店替此商品補貨時收到通知。','Allow sign-ups'=>'允許註冊','Customer stock notifications'=>'顧客庫存通知','Verification email sent to "%s".'=>'驗證電子郵件已傳送至「%s」。','Notification sent to "%s".'=>'通知已傳送至「%s」。','Failed to send notification. Please make sure that the listed product is available.'=>'無法傳送通知。 請確認所列商品有貨。','Notification updated.'=>'通知已更新。','Notification created.'=>'通知已建立。','A <a href="%s">notification</a> for the same product and customer already exists in your database.'=>'資料庫已存在相同商品和顧客的<a href="%s">通知</a>。','Please select a customer.'=>'請選取顧客。','Please select a product.'=>'請選取商品。','Notifications per page'=>'每頁通知數','Stock Notifications'=>'庫存通知','notifications_status%s notification deleted.'=>'%s 個通知已刪除。','notifications_status%s notification updated.'=>'%s 個通知已更新。','Notification not found.'=>'找不到通知。','Notification deleted.'=>'通知已刪除。','Filter by date'=>'依日期篩選','notifications_statusPending <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'待確認 <span class="count">(%s 個)</span>','notifications_statusCancelled <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'已取消 <span class="count">(%s 個)</span>','notifications_statusSent <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'已傳送 <span class="count">(%s 個)</span>','notifications_statusActive <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'已啟用 <span class="count">(%s 個)</span>','notifications_statusAll <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'全部 <span class="count">(%s 個)</span>','Select customer&hellip;'=>'選取顧客...','Select product&hellip;'=>'選取商品...','Invalid 