ing.'=>'重設供應商狀態/帳號，並重新提出申請的連結。','The URL to POST to disable the test account for the payment gateway.'=>'停用付款閘道測試帳號的 POST URL。','The link to disable the test account for the payment gateway.'=>'停用付款閘道測試帳號的連結。','Action to disable the test account currently in use'=>'可停用目前使用中測試帳號的動作','Action to reset the onboarding process, either partially, for a certain step, or fully.'=>'重設申請流程的動作，可部分重設特定步驟，也可重設整個流程。','block keywordsingle product'=>'單一商品','block descriptionDisplay a single product of your choice with full control over its presentation.'=>'顯示你所選的單一商品，並完全掌控呈現方式。','block titleProduct'=>'商品','block descriptionEnable customers to filter the product collection by selecting one or more taxonomy terms, such as categories, brands, or tags.'=>'允許顧客選取一或多個分類字詞 (例如分類、品牌或標籤)，以便篩選商品系列。','block titleTaxonomy Filter'=>'分類法篩選條件','block keywordpayment methods'=>'付款方式','block keywordpayments'=>'付款','block descriptionDisplay icons for available payment methods.'=>'顯示可用付款方式的圖示。','block titlePayment Method Icons'=>'付款方式圖示','block descriptionDisplay a Mini-Cart widget.'=>'顯示迷你購物車小工具。','block titleMini-Cart Contents'=>'迷你購物車內容','Shipment %s'=>'貨件 %s','Pending items'=>'待確認的項目','You can access to more details of your order by visiting My Account > Orders and select the order you wish to see the latest status of the delivery.'=>'你可以前往「我的帳號」>「訂單」選取欲檢視最新交貨狀態的訂單，藉此存取訂單的更多詳細資料。','Tracking URL'=>'追蹤 URL','Fulfillment summary'=>'履行項目摘要','You can access to more details of your order by visiting <a href="%s" target="_blank">My Account > Orders</a> and select the order you wish to see the latest status of the delivery.'=>'你可以前往<a href="%s" target="_blank">「我的帳號」>「訂單」</a>選取欲檢視最新交貨狀態的訂單，藉此存取訂單的更多詳細資料。','Track your shipment'=>'追蹤你的貨件','Tracking Number'=>'追蹤號碼','No tracking information available for this fulfillment at the moment.'=>'目前此履行項目沒有可用的追蹤資訊。','Here’s the latest info we have:'=>'以下為最新資訊：','Some details of your shipment have recently been updated. This may include tracking information, 