en the merchant updates a fulfillment for the order. The notification isn’t sent for draft fulfillments.'=>'商家更新訂單的履行項目時，系統會傳送履行項目已更新的電子郵件給顧客。 完成履行項目草稿時不會傳送通知。','This tool will repair the coupons lookup table data with missing discount amounts. This process may take a while.'=>'此工具會修復缺少折扣金額的優惠券查詢表資料。 此程序可能需耗時一段時間。','Fulfillment updated'=>'履行項目已更新','If you have any questions or notice anything unexpected, feel free to reach out to our support team through your account or reply to this email.'=>'如果你有任何問題或注意到任何意外狀況，歡迎透過你的帳號聯絡我們的支援團隊，或回覆這封電子郵件。','One of your shipments has been removed'=>'已移除其中一個貨件','A shipment from {site_title} order {order_number} has been cancelled'=>'已取消「{site_title}」訂單 ({order_number}) 的貨件','Fulfillment deleted emails are sent to the customer when the merchant cancels an already fulfilled fulfillment. The notification isn’t sent for draft fulfillments.'=>'商家取消已完成的履行項目時，系統會傳送履行項目已刪除的電子郵件給顧客。 完成履行項目草稿時不會傳送通知。','Fulfillment deleted'=>'履行項目已刪除','Expected Delivery'=>'預期送件','Service'=>'服務','Please note that couriers may need some time to provide the latest shipping information.'=>'請注意，快遞業者可能需要一段時間才能提供最新的運送資訊。','Your item is on the way!'=>'你的商品馬上就到！','An item from {site_title} order {order_number} has been fulfilled!'=>'已履行「{site_title}」訂單 ({order_number}) 的項目！','Fulfillment created emails are sent to the customer when the merchant creates a fulfillment for the order, and marks it as fulfilled. The notification isn’t sent for draft fulfillments.'=>'商家建立訂單的履行項目時，系統會傳送履行項目已建立的電子郵件給顧客，並將訂單標示為已履行。 完成履行項目草稿時不會傳送通知。','Fulfillment created'=>'履行項目已建立','To offer local pickup, configure your pickup locations in the <a href=\'%s\'>local pickup settings</a>.'=>'如要使用當地取貨服務，請在<a href=\'%s\'>當地取貨設定</a>中設定取貨位置。','block descriptionUse blocks to create an "Add to cart" area that\'s customized for different product types, such as variable and grouped. '=>'使用區塊建立為不同商品類別自訂的「加入購物車」區域，類別包含多款式商品和組合商品。 ','block titleAdd to Cart + Options (Beta)'=>'加入購物車 + 選項 (測試版)','block descri