endering halted]'=>'[商品說明轉譯已暫停]','The admin note type prop is deprecated.'=>'管理員備註類別屬性已過時。','Whether blueprint imports are currently allowed'=>'目前是否允許匯入藍圖','Blueprint imports are disabled'=>'已停用藍圖匯入功能','Your review is awaiting moderation. This is a preview; your review will be visible after it has been approved.'=>'你的評論正在等候審核。 這是預覽模式；核准後即可檢視你的評論。','Sorry, you cannot import WooCommerce Blueprints.'=>'很抱歉，無法匯入 WooCommerce 藍圖。','Your store emails have had an upgrade!'=>'你的商店電子郵件已升級！','Includes all the installed plugins.'=>'包含所有已安裝的外掛程式。','Sorry, you cannot export WooCommerce Blueprints.'=>'很抱歉，無法匯出 WooCommerce 藍圖。','Remove %s coupon'=>'移除優惠券「%s」','Limit results to those with a name or SKU that partial matches a string. This argument takes precedence over \'search\', \'sku\' and \'search_sku\'.'=>'將結果限制為與字串部分相符的名稱或貨號。 這個引數的優先順序高於 \'search\'、\'sku\' 和 \'search_sku\'。','Limit results to those with a SKU that partial matches a string. This argument takes precedence over \'sku\'.'=>'將結果限制為與字串部分相符的貨號。 此引數的優先順序高於 \'sku\'。','Brand slug.'=>'品牌代稱。','Brand name.'=>'品牌名稱。','Brand ID.'=>'品牌 ID。','List of brands.'=>'品牌清單。','Limit result set to orders created via specific sources (e.g. checkout, admin).'=>'透過特定來源 (例如結帳、管理員) 所建立的訂單限制結果集。','Cost of Goods Sold data. Only present for product refund line items.'=>'銷貨成本資料。 僅顯示商品退款細項。','Total value of the Cost of Goods Sold for the refund.'=>'此退款的銷貨成本總值。','Enabled features.'=>'已啟用的功能。','Server architecture.'=>'伺服器架構。','Value of the Cost of Goods Sold for the refund item.'=>'退款項目的銷貨成本值。','Order refunded emails are sent to customers when their POS orders are refunded.'=>'訂單退款電子郵件會在 POS 訂單退款時寄送給顧客。','POS refunded order'=>'已退款的 POS 訂單','Time of payment:'=>'付款時間：','Auth code:'=>'驗證碼：','Change due:'=>'找零金額：','Let customers know once their POS order is complete.'=>'在 POS 訂單處理完成時通知顧客。','Cost per unit: %s'=>'每單位費用：%s','Sorry, coupon "%1$s" is not applicable to the categories: %2$s.'=>'很抱歉，折價券「%1$s」不能用於分類：%2$s','Sorry, coupon "%1$s" is not applicable to the products: %2$s.'=>'很抱歉，折價券「%1$s」不能用於商品：%2$s','Let customers know when a full or partial refund is on its way to them for their POS order.'=>'在核發 POS 訂單的全額或部分退款時通知顧客。','Order complete emails are sent to customers when their POS orders are marked completed.'=>'POS 訂單標示為完成時，將會寄送訂單完成電子郵件給顧客。','POS completed order'=>'已完成的 POS 訂單','Usage limit for coupon "%s" has been reached. Please try again after some time, or contact us for help.'=>'折價券「%s」的使用次數已達上限。 請稍後再試一次，或聯絡我們尋求協助。','Coupon "%s" has expired.'=>'折價券「%s」已過期。','Features that are currently enabled.'=>'目前已啟用的功能。','Enabled features:'=>'已啟用的功能：','Information about the operating system your server is running.'=>'伺服器執行中作業系統的相關資訊。','Server architecture'=>'伺服器架構','This tool allows you to generate and download a CSV file containing the selected products.'=>'此工具能協助你產生並下載包含所選商品清單的 CSV 檔案。','Hide shipping rates when free shipping is available'=>'有免運費活動時隱藏運費','Revert to legacy template'=>'還原為舊版範本','The maximum spend for coupon "%1$s" is %2$s.'=>'折價券「%1$s」的最高消費額為 %2$s。','The minimum spend for coupon "%1$s" is %2$s.'=>'折價券「%1$s」的消費門檻為 %2$s。','Usage limit for coupon "%s" has been reached.'=>'折價券「%s」的使用次數已達上限。','You are about to export %1$d product. To export all products, <a href="%2$s">clear your selection</a>.'=>'即將匯出 %1$d 項商品。 若要匯出所有商品，請<a href="%2$s">清除選取項目</a>。','Are you sure want to revert to legacy? Doing so will erase any changes you’ve made to your new email templates, and will restore your previous email designs.'=>'確定要還原為舊版？ 若繼續進行，系統會清除你對新電子郵件範本進行的所有變更，並還原為前一個電子郵件設計。','Keep legacy template'=>'保留舊版範本','Switch to new template'=>'切換為新的範本','Previewing new template designs. You can customize and test your emails and switch to the new template whenever you are ready.'=>'預覽新的範本設計。 你可以自訂並測試電子郵件，並在準備就緒時切換到新範本。','Email improvements button'=>'電子郵件強化按鈕','Try new templates'=>'試用新範本','You can specify a <a href="#" class="switch-to-general-tab">default value</a> for all variations'=>'你可以為所有款式指定<a href="#" class="switch-to-general-tab">預設值</a>','Cost Total'=>'費用總計','Your site is currently connected to WooCommerce.com using <b>%1$s</b>, but your actual site URL is <b>%2$s</b>. To fix this, please reconnect your site to <b>WooCommerce.com</b> to ensure everything works correctly.'=>'你的網站目前已使用「<b>%1$s</b>」連結至 WooCommerce.com，但實際網站 URL 為「<b>%2$s</b>」。 若要修正此問題，請將你的網站重新連結至 <b>WooCommerce.com</b>，確保一切都能正常運作。','Try our new email templates!'=>'試試我們的新電子郵件範本！','WooCommerce.com API returned HTTP status code %d.'=>'WooCommerce.com API 已傳回 HTTP 狀態碼「%d」。','The plugin for your subscription couldn\'t be activated.'=>'無法啟用訂閱的外掛程式。','The plugin for your subscription has been activated.'=>'已啟用訂閱的外掛程式。','API response is missing required elements, or they are in the wrong form.'=>'API 回應缺少必要元素，或元素格式錯誤。','We couldn\'t find a preview for this product.'=>'找不到此商品的預覽。','There was an error rendering the email preview.'=>'轉譯電子郵件預覽時發生錯誤。','There was an error rendering the email preview. This doesn\'t affect actual email delivery. Please contact the extension author for assistance.'=>'轉譯電子郵件預覽時發生錯誤。 這不會影響實際的電子郵件傳送狀況。 請聯絡擴充功能作者尋求協助。','Loading status data...'=>'正在載入狀態資料…','Export %d selected'=>'匯出 %d 個已選取的內容','You have exceeded the request limit. Please try again after a few minutes.'=>'你已超過要求上限。 請稍待幾分鐘後再試一次。','WooCommerce.com API returned an invalid response.'=>'WooCommerce.com API 傳回無效的回應。','Authentication failed. Please try again after a few minutes. If the issue persists, disconnect your store from WooCommerce.com and reconnect.'=>'驗證失敗。 請稍待幾分鐘後再試一次。 如果問題持續發生，請中斷你的商店與 WooCommerce.com 的連結，然後重新連結一次。','File path is not a valid upload path.'=>'檔案路徑不是有效的上傳路徑。','Unix timestamp representing when the incentive was dismissed.'=>'代表獎勵措施已撤除的 Unix 時間戳記。','The dismissals list for the incentive. Each dismissal entry includes a context and a timestamp. The `all` entry means the incentive was dismissed for all contexts.'=>'此獎勵措施的撤除清單。 每個撤除的條目都包含內容與時間戳記。 `all` 條目是指在所有情況下撤除此獎勵措施。','Return to shipping'=>'返回運送','Font size nameextra-large