uped product IDs, if applicable.'=>'組合商品 ID 清單 (如有)。','List of brands, if applicable.'=>'品牌清單 (如有)。','Number of reviews for products of this brand.'=>'此品牌的商品評論數量。','Brand image.'=>'品牌形象。','Order notes.'=>'訂單備註。','Selected payment method for the order.'=>'選取的訂單付款方式。','Additional fields related to the order.'=>'與訂單相關的其他欄位。','Billing email updated to %s.'=>'帳單電子郵件已更新為 %s。','Order already has a billing email.'=>'訂單已有帳單電子郵件。','Order Actions'=>'訂單動作','A unique ID string for the email template.'=>'電子郵件範本的唯一 ID 字串。','Limit result set to products assigned a set of tag IDs or slugs, separated by commas.'=>'將結果集限制為獲派一組標籤 ID 或代稱 (以逗號分隔) 的商品。','Operator to compare product taxonomies terms.'=>'比較商品分類法標籤的運算子。','Limit result set to products assigned a set of taxonomies IDs or slugs, separated by commas.'=>'將結果集限制為獲派一組分類法 ID 或代稱 (以逗號分隔) 的商品。','Operator to compare product brand terms.'=>'比較商品品牌字詞的運算子。','Limit result set to products assigned a set of brand IDs or slugs, separated by commas.'=>'將結果集限制為獲派一組品牌 ID 或代稱 (以逗號分隔) 的商品。','Limit result set to products assigned a set of category IDs or slugs, separated by commas.'=>'將結果集限制為獲派一組分類 ID 或代稱 (以逗號分隔) 的商品。','Invalid brand slug.'=>'品牌代稱無效。','Invalid brand ID.'=>'品牌 ID 無效。','%s is not a valid template for this order.'=>'%s 並非此訂單的有效範本。','A description of the purpose of the email template.'=>'電子郵件範本用途說明。','The display name of the email template.'=>'電子郵件範本顯示名稱。','Email Template'=>'電子郵件範本','Enable blueprint to import and export settings in bulk'=>'啟用藍圖以大量匯入和匯出設定','Homepage URL'=>'首頁 URL','Site'=>'網站','Site Title'=>'網站標題','Woo Email Template'=>'Woo 電子郵件範本','Woo Email Content Pattern'=>'Woo 電子郵件內容版面配置','The ID of the template to use for sending the email.'=>'傳送電子郵件所用之範本的 ID。','Whether to update the billing email of the order, even if it already has one.'=>'是否更新訂單的帳單電子郵件 (即使訂單已有電子郵件亦然)。','Block Email Editor (alpha)'=>'區塊電子郵件編輯器 (英文字母)','Enable modern email design for transactional emails'=>'為交易電子郵件啟用現代電子郵件設計','⚠ Usage tracking must be enabled to