lay a short description about a product.'=>'顯示簡短的商品說明。','block titleProduct Summary'=>'商品摘要','block descriptionDisplay an input field customers can use to select the number of products to add to their cart. '=>'顯示顧客可使用的輸入欄位，選取要加入購物車的商品數量。 ','Products in cart'=>'購物車商品','Action needed'=>'需要採取行動','Sync with theme'=>'與佈景主題同步','WooCommerce Settings'=>'WooCommerce 設定','Sorry, your order on %1$s was unsuccessful. Your order details are below, with a link to try your payment again: %2$s'=>'很抱歉，你的「%1$s」訂單處理失敗。 你的訂單詳細資料如下，附上連結供你嘗試重新付款：%2$s','Order status slug.'=>'訂單狀態代稱。','Order statuses not found'=>'找不到訂單狀態','HPOS Data Caching'=>'HPOS 資料快取','Rate limit Checkout'=>'費率限制結帳','Stock availability class.'=>'庫存供應狀況類別。','Stock availability text.'=>'庫存供應狀況文字。','Information about the product\'s availability.'=>'商品供應狀況的相關資訊。','Enables rate limiting for Checkout place order and Store API /checkout endpoint. To further control this, refer to <a href="%s" target="_blank">rate limiting documentation</a>.'=>'針對結帳下單及商店 API/結帳端點，啟用費率限制。 若要進一步控制費率限制，請參閱<a href="%s" target="_blank">費率限制文件</a>。','Securely accept credit and debit cards with one low rate, no surprise fees (custom rates available). Sell in store and track sales and inventory in one place.'=>'以單一低費率方式安全地接受信用卡和簽帳金融卡付款，不收取額外費用 (可自訂費率)。 實體店面銷售，並集中追蹤銷售和庫存狀況。','Enable PayU\'s exclusive plugin for WooCommerce to start accepting payments in 100+ payment methods available in India including credit cards, debit cards, UPI, & more!'=>'啟用 PayU 的 WooCommerce 專屬外掛程式，開始收取印度超過 100 種付款方式的款項，包括信用卡、簽帳金融卡和 UPI 等！','Clearpay allows customers to receive products immediately and pay for purchases over four installments, always interest-free.'=>'Clearpay 可讓顧客立即收到商品，並分四期付款 (一律享零利率)。','Clearpay'=>'Clearpay','Affirm\'s tailored Buy Now Pay Later programs remove price as a barrier, turning browsers into buyers, increasing average order value, and expanding your customer base.'=>'Affirm 精心設計的「先買後付」方案消除了價格障礙，可將瀏覽者變成買家，從而提升平均訂單金額並拓展你的顧客群。','Accept payments with Woo'=>'透過 Woo 接受付款','Accept credit and debit cards on your WooCommerce store with advanced features like partial refunds, full/partial captures, and 3D Secure security.'=>'搭載部分退款、全額/部分請款及 3D 安全防護等先進功能，讓你的 WooCommerce 商店能接受信用卡和簽帳金融卡付款。','Tilopay'=>'Tilopay','Stripe'=>'Stripe','PayU India'=>'PayU (印度)','Payoneer Checkout is the next generation of payment processing platforms, giving merchants around the world the solutions and direction they need to succeed in today\'s hyper-competitive global market.'=>'Payoneer Checkout 是新一代付款處理平台，為世界各地商家提供所需的解決方案和指引，讓他們在現今競爭激烈的全球市場中締造成功佳績。','Viva.com Smart Checkout'=>'Viva.com 智慧結帳','A European payments solution that allows you to accept payments in over 25 countries and multiple currencies.'=>'這是一款歐洲的付款方案，可接受超過 25 個國家/地區多種幣別的付款。','Credit/debit cards, Apple Pay, Google Pay, and more.'=>'信用卡/簽帳金融卡、Apple Pay 與 Google Pay 等。','PayPal Payments lets you offer PayPal, Venmo (US only), Pay Later options and more.'=>'PayPal Payments 提供 PayPal、Venmo (僅限美國)、先買後付等選項。','Safe and secure payments using your customer\'s PayPal account.'=>'使用客戶的 PayPal 帳戶進行安全且可靠的付款。','Paymob is a leading payment gateway in the Middle East and Africa. Accept payments online and in-store with Paymob.'=>'Paymob 在中東和非洲是熱門的付款閘道。 接受透過 Paymob 進行線上和店內付款。','Paymob'=>'Paymob','The Payfast extension for WooCommerce enables you to accept payments by Credit Card and EFT via one of South Africa\'s most popular payment gateways. No setup fees or monthly subscription costs. Selecting this extension will configure your store to use South African rands as the selected currency.'=>'使用 WooCommerce 的 PayFast 擴充功能，便能透過南非其中一個熱門付款閘道，使用信用卡和 EFT 接收付款。 無須支付設定費或訂閱月費。 若選擇此擴充功能，你的商店會設為使用南非蘭特作為所選貨幣。','The category of the suggestion.'=>'此建議的分類。','The tags associated with the suggestion.'=>'與此建議相關的標籤。','The URL of the icon (square aspect ratio).'=>'圖示的 URL (矩形長寬比)。','The URL of the image.'=>'圖片的 URL。','The description of the suggestion.'=>'此建議的說明。','The title of the suggestion.'=>'此建議的標題。','The type of the suggestion.'=>'此建議的類型。','The priority of the suggestion.'=>'此建議的優先順序。','The unique identifier for the suggestion.'=>'此建議的唯一識別碼。','The URL to hide the suggestion.'=>'隱藏此建議的 URL。','The link to hide the suggestion.'=>'隱藏此建議的連結。','The URL to dismiss the incentive.'=>'撤除此獎勵的 URL。','The link to dismiss the incentive.'=>'撤除此獎勵的連結。','Context ID in which the incentive was dismissed.'=>'撤除此獎勵的內容 ID。','The badge label for the incentive.'=>'此獎勵的徽章標籤。','The URL to the terms and conditions for the incentive.'=>'此獎勵適用的條款與條件 URL。','The call to action label for the incentive.'=>'此獎勵的行動呼籲標籤。','Your trusted payments partner in Asia and around the world.'=>'你在亞洲及全球備受信賴的付款合作夥伴。','Antom'=>'Antom','A suggestion with full details.'=>'附上完整詳細資料的建議。','The short description of the incentive. It can contain stylistic HTML.'=>'此獎勵的簡短說明。 內含 HTML 樣式。','The incentive description. It can contain stylistic HTML.'=>'獎勵說明。 內含 HTML 樣式。','The incentive title. It can contain stylistic HTML.'=>'獎勵標題。 內含 HTML 樣式。','The incentive promo ID. This ID need to be fed into the onboarding flow.'=>'獎勵宣傳 ID。 請將此 ID 送入申請流程。','The incentive unique ID. This ID needs to be used for incentive dismissals.'=>'獎勵的唯一 ID。 此 ID 必須用於獎勵撤銷。','The active incentive for the provider.'=>'供應商使用中的獎勵。','The suggestion ID matching this provider.'=>'建議 ID 與此供應商相符。','Tag associated with the provider.'=>'與供應商相關的標籤。','The tags associated with the provider.'=>'與供應商相關的標籤。','The URL of the payment method icon or a base64-encoded SVG image.'=>'付款方式圖示或基底 64 編碼 SVG 圖片的 URL。','The description of the payment method. It can contain basic HTML.'=>'付款方式說明。 內含基本 HTML。','The title of the payment method. Does not include HTML tags.'=>'付款方式標題。 不含 HTML 標籤。','Whether the payment method should be required (and force-enabled) or not.'=>'付款方式是否為必要 (且強制啟用)。','Whether the payment method should be recommended as enabled or not.'=>'付款方式是否應建議為啟用。','The sort order of the payment method.'=>'付款方式的排序。','The unique identifier for the payment method.'=>'付款方式的唯一識別碼。','The details for a recommended payment method.'=>'建議付款方式的詳細資料。','The state of the onboarding process.'=>'申請流程的狀態。','The management details of the provider.'=>'供應商的管理詳細資料。','Whether the provider is in dev mode. Having this true usually leads to forcing test payments. '=>'供應商是否處於開發模式。 若為 true，通常會導致強制測試付款。 ','Whether the provider is in test mode for payments processing.'=>'供應商是否處於付款處理的測試模式。','Whether the provider needs setup.'=>'供應商是否需要進行設定。','Whether the provider is enabled for use on checkout.'=>'供應商是否已在結帳時啟用。','The general state of the provider with regards to it\'s payments processing.'=>'關於供應商付款處理的一般狀態。','The URL of the link.'=>'連結 URL。','The type of the link.'=>'連結類型。','Links for the provider.'=>'供應商適用的連結。','The URL of the provider icon (square aspect ratio - 72px by 72px).'=>'供應商圖示的 URL (矩形長寬比：72px x 72px)。','The URL of the provider image.'=>'供應商圖片的 URL。','The status of the plugin.'=>'外掛程式的狀態。','The plugin main file. This is a relative path to the plugins directory.'=>'外掛程式的主要檔案。 此為相對於外掛程式目錄的路徑。','The list of recommended payment methods details for the payment gateway.'=>'付款閘道建議付款方式詳細資料的清單。','The URL to start/continue onboarding for the payment gateway.'=>'付款閘道的開始/繼續申請流程 URL。','The start/continue onboarding link for the payment gateway.'=>'付款閘道的開始/繼續申請流程連結。','Onboarding-related details for the provider.'=>'供應商的申請流程相關詳細資料。','The URL to the settings page for the payment gateway.'=>'付款閘道設定頁面的 URL。','The link to the settings page for the payment gateway.'=>'付款閘道設定頁面的連結。','Whether the provider has a payments processing account connected.'=>'供應商是否已連結付款處理帳號。','Whether the onboarding process is completed.'=>'申請流程是否完成。','Whether the onboarding process is started.'=>'申請流程是否開始。','The slug of the plugin.'=>'外掛程式代稱。','The type of the plugin.'=>'外掛程式類型。','Supported features for this provider.'=>'此供應商的支援功能。','The description of the category.'=>'此分類的說明。','The title of the category.'=>'此分類的標題。','The priority of the category.'=>'此分類的優先順序。','The unique identifier for the ca