ess checkout feature.'=>'輕鬆付款：你可使用 WooPay 這項全新的快速結帳功能。','A list of plugins to install'=>'要安裝的外掛程式清單','System status theme info cache cleared.'=>'已清除系統狀態佈景主題資訊快取。','This tool will empty the system status theme info cache.'=>'此工具將清空系統狀態佈景主題資訊快取。','Log PayPal events such as IPN requests and review them on the <a href="%s">Logs screen</a>. Note: this may log personal information. We recommend using this for debugging purposes only and deleting the logs when finished.'=>'記錄 IPN 要求等 PayPal 事件，並在<a href="%s">記錄畫面</a>中檢視。 注意：這可能會記錄個人資訊。 我們建議僅將此用於偵錯目的，並在完成時予以刪除。','&ldquo;%s&rdquo; has been added to your cart'=>'「%s」已新增至你的購物車','Clear system status theme info cache'=>'清除系統狀態佈景主題資訊快取','Invalid file type for a CSV import.'=>'此檔案類型無法匯入 CSV。','ISBN'=>'ISBN','International Standard Book Number'=>'國際標準書號','EAN'=>'EAN','European Article Number'=>'國際商品條碼','UPC'=>'UPC','Universal Product Code'=>'國際通用商品條碼','GTIN'=>'GTIN','Global Trade Item Number'=>'全球交易品項識別碼','%1$s, %2$s, %3$s, or %4$s'=>'%1$s、%2$s、%3$s 或 %4$s','File path provided for import is invalid.'=>'提供的匯入檔案路徑無效。','Create an account with %s'=>'建立「%s」的帳號','Add %s'=>'新增 %s','Please create a password for your account.'=>'請為你的帳號建立密碼。','Remote Logging'=>'遠端記錄','Google for WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce 的 Google 整合服務','
