h WooPayments — all from one dashboard, without needing multiple extensions and logins.'=>'全球最愛的「先買後付」以及其他更多選項，都在 WooPayments 供你隨時隨地使用，全在同一個儀表板上任你操作，無須動用多個擴充功能或登入。','Activate BNPL instantly on WooPayments'=>'立即在 WooPayments 啟用 BNPL','Enhance your store with extensions'=>'活用擴充功能強化商店','Net Sales'=>'淨銷售額','Table cell format.'=>'表格儲存格格式。','Find your shade'=>'找尋你的太陽眼鏡','Our services'=>'我們的服務','Create anything'=>'創造一切','Meet us'=>'認識我們','Explore our exclusive collection of sunglasses, crafted to elevate your look and safeguard your eyes. Find your perfect pair and see the world through a new lens.'=>'探索我們獨家製作的太陽眼鏡系列，不只讓你的外表加分，還可保護你的眼睛。 找尋一副完美眼鏡，用新視角大開眼界。','Navigating life\'s intricate fabric, choices unfold paths to the extraordinary, demanding creativity, curiosity, and courage for a truly fulfilling journey.'=>'探索生活所編織的精細紋路，不同選擇開展出非凡、高標準的創造力、好奇心與勇氣，心曠神怡的旅程就在眼前。','Our passion is crafting mindful moments with locally sourced, organic, and sustainable products. We\'re more than a store; we\'re your path to a community-driven, eco-friendly lifestyle that embraces premium quality.'=>'我們熱愛透過在地供應、有機且永續商品，創造正念時刻。 我們不只是一家商店，更將帶你通往社區導向且環境友善的生活方式，並擁抱高品質生活。','Committed to a greener lifestyle'=>'致力打造更友善環境的生活方式','Unidentified action %s: we were unable to mark this action as having completed. It may may have been deleted by another process.'=>'不明的動作 %s：我們無法將此動作勾選為已完成。 可能已在其他程序中刪除。','Unidentified action %s: we were unable to mark this action as having failed. It may may have been deleted by another process.'=>'不明的動作 %s：我們無法將此動作勾選為失敗。 可能已在其他程序中刪除。','Unidentified action %s: we were unable to determine the date of this action. It may may have been deleted by another process.'=>'不明的動作 %s：我們無法決定此動作的日期。 可能已在其他程序中刪除。','Unidentified action %s: we were unable to delete this action. It may may have been deleted by another process.'=>'不明的動作 %s：我們無法刪除此動作。 可能已在其他程序中刪除。','Unidentified action %s: we were unable to cancel this action. It may may have been deleted by another process.'=>'不明的動作 %s：我們無法取消此動作。 可能已在其他程序中刪除。','GTIN, UPC, EAN or ISBN.'=>'GTIN、UPC、EAN 或 ISBN。','Stock Keeping Unit.'=>'貨號。','Invalid slug.'=>'無效的代稱。','Order query argument (%s) is not supported on the current order datastore.'=>'目前的訂單資料存放區不支援訂單查詢引數 (%s)。','Order sort items ascending or descending.'=>'以遞增或遞減方式排序項目。','Legacy REST API enabled?'=>'是否已啟用舊版 REST API？','An unexpected error occurred while generating the refund.'=>'產生退款時發生不明錯誤。','Does your site have the Legacy REST API enabled?'=>'你的網站是否已啟用舊版 REST API？','Legacy API enabled'=>'已啟用舊版 API','Local pickup: Manage existing pickup locations in the <a href="%s">Local pickup settings page</a>.'=>'自行取貨：在<a href="%s">「自行取貨」設定頁面</a>管理現有的取貨地點。','Repeat fetches made within a reasonable window of time (by default, 30 minutes) will not be counted twice. This is a generally reasonably way to enforce download limits in relation to ranged requests. %1$sLearn more.%2$s'=>'系統不會重複計算合理時段內 (預設為 30 分鐘) 的重複擷取。 這是在執行與範圍要求相關的下載限制時，較為合理的方式。 %1$s深入了解。%2$s','This coupon is password protected. WooCommerce does not support password protection for coupons. You can temporarily hide a coupon by making it private. Alternatively, usage limits and restrictions can be configured below.'=>'這張優惠券受密碼保護。 WooCommerce 並未支援優惠券密碼保護。 若你想隱藏，可以暫時將優惠券設為私人。 或者你可以在下方設定使用次數上限與限制。','Send password setup link (recommended)'=>'傳送密碼設定連結 (建議)','Allow customers to create an account'=>'顧客可建立帳號：','Customers can create an account before placing their order.'=>'顧客可在下單前建立帳號。','During checkout'=>'結帳期間','Enable log-in during checkout'=>'啟用在結帳期間登入的功能','New users receive an email to set up their password.'=>'新使用者會收到密碼設定電子郵件。','Account creation options'=>'帳號建立選項','On "My account" page'=>'「我的帳號」頁面','Enable guest checkout (recommended)'=>'啟用訪客結帳功能 (建議)','Delete fee'=>'刪除費用','Edit fee'=>'編輯費用','Enter a barcode or any other identifier unique to this product. It can help you list this product on other channels or marketplaces.'=>'請輸入條碼或此商品任一不重複識別碼， 這可協助你將此商品上架於其他通路或市集。','Delete shipping'=>'刪除貨運方式','Edit shipping'=>'編輯貨運方式','Invalid or duplicated GTIN, UPC, EAN or ISBN.'=>'無效或重複的 GTIN、UPC、EAN 或 ISBN。','Count partial downloads'=>'計算部分下載','Please enter only numbers and hyphens (-).'=>'請只輸入數字與連字號 (-)。','Count downloads even if only part of a file is fetched.'=>'即使僅擷取到檔案的一部分，也會計入下載次數。','Services'=>'服務','Translatable Label'=>'可翻譯的標籤','View order number %s'=>'檢視訂單編號 %s','This setting only works when product data is stored in the posts table.'=>'唯有商品資料儲存在文章表格內時，才可使用本設定。','Optimized updates'=>'經過最佳化的更新項目','Uses much more performant queries to update the lookup table, but may not be compatible with some extensions.'=>'使用更多高效能查詢來更新查閱表格，但某些擴充功能可能不相容。','Orders are automatically put in the Refunded status when an admin or shop manager has fully refunded the order’s value after payment.'=>'若管理員或商店經理於款項付清後以訂單價格全額退還，則訂單會自動進入「已退款」狀態。','The order was canceled by an admin or the customer.'=>'此訂單已由管理員或顧客取消。','Draft orders are created when customers start the checkout process while the block version of the checkout is in place.'=>'若顧客在開始結帳程序時仍保有結帳的區塊版本，則系統會建立訂單草稿。','The customer’s payment failed or was declined, and no payment has been successfully made.'=>'顧客付款失敗或遭拒，因此款項並未成功支付。','Order fulfilled and complete.'=>'訂單已履行並完成。','Payment has been received (paid), and the stock has been reduced. The order is awaiting fulfillment.'=>'款項已收取 (支付)，庫存也已減少。 此訂單正在等候履行。','The order has been received, but no payment has been made. Pending payment orders are generally awaiting customer action.'=>'已收到訂單，但沒有收到款項。 待處理付款的訂單通常仍在等待顧客的動作。','Compatibility mode disabled.'=>'已停用相容模式。','Compatibility mode enabled.'=>'已啟用相容模式。','Compatibility mode is already disabled.'=>'相容模式已停用。','Compatibility mode is already enabled.'=>'相容模式已啟用。','HPOS tables do not exist.'=>'HPOS 表格不存在。','Wrong response received from the Patterns Toolkit API: try again later.'=>'版面配置工具組 API 傳回錯誤回應：請稍後再試一次。','Empty response received from the Patterns Toolkit API.'=>'版面配置工具組 API 傳回空白回應。','The order is awaiting payment confirmation. Stock is reduced, 