ct form'=>'已上傳至此商品表單','Insert into product form'=>'插入至商品表單','Use as product form image'=>'用為商品表單圖片','Remove product form image'=>'移除商品表單圖片','Set product form image'=>'設定商品表單圖片','Product form image'=>'商品表單圖片','Parent product form'=>'上層商品表單','No product forms found in trash'=>'垃圾桶裡找不到商品表單','No product forms found'=>'找不到商品表單','Search product forms'=>'搜尋商品表單','View product forms'=>'檢視商品表單','View product form'=>'檢視商品表單','New product form'=>'新商品表單','Edit product form'=>'編輯商品表單','Add new product form'=>'新增新商品表單','Admin menu nameProduct Forms'=>'商品表單','All Product Form'=>'所有商品表單','Product Form'=>'商品表單','Product Forms'=>'商品表單','Contains the <strong>%1$s</strong> block'=>'包含「<strong>%1$s</strong>」區塊','Contains the <strong>%1$s</strong> shortcode'=>'包含「<strong>%1$s</strong>」短代碼','This page\'s content is overridden by custom template content'=>'此頁內容已由自訂範本內容覆蓋','Page contains both the %1$s shortcode and the %2$s block.'=>'頁面同時包含「%1$s」短代碼和「%2$s」區塊。','Write-only keys do not prevent clients from seeing information about the entities they are updating.'=>'若客戶打算對特定實體加以更新，唯寫金鑰無法防止客戶看到實體相關資訊。','Add a meaningful description, including a note of the person, company or app you are sharing the key with.'=>'請新增有意義的描述，並註記你要打算分享金鑰的人物、公司或應用程式。','Stick to one key per client: this makes it easier to revoke access in the future for a single client, without causing disruption for others.'=>'每個客戶請以一個金鑰為限：這有助你於日後輕鬆針對單一客戶撤銷存取權，不會對其他客戶造成影響。','API keys open up access to potentially sensitive information. Only share them with organizations you trust.'=>'API 金鑰具備能開啟可能為敏感資訊的存取權。 請只與你信任的組織分享金鑰。','block titleProduct Quantity (Beta)'=>'商品數量 (測試版)','block titleProduct Collection'=>'商品系列','block descriptionLet shoppers filter products displayed on the page.'=>'讓買家篩選頁面顯示的商品。','block titleDelivery'=>'到貨','block descriptionAllows shoppers to clear active filters.'=>'允許購物者清除使用中的篩選條件。','Plugins'=>'外掛程式','You have <strong>%1$s Woo extension subscriptions</strong> that expired. <a href="%2$s">Renew</a> to continue receiving updates and streamlined support.'=>'你有 <strong>%1$s 個 Woo 擴充功能訂閱項目</strong>已到期。 請<a href="%2$s">續訂</a>，如此才能繼續收到更新和簡化又便捷的支援。','One of your subscriptions for <strong>%1$s</strong> has expired. <a href="%3$s">%4$s</a> to continue receiving updates and streamlined support.'=>'你其中一個「<strong>%1$s</strong>」訂閱已到期。請<a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>，如此才能繼續收到更新和簡化又便捷的支援。','Creative format'=>'建立格式','Source platform'=>'來源平台','%d is not of a valid order type.'=>'「%d」並非有效的訂單類型。','Sync orders now'=>'立即同步訂單','Stop sync'=>'停止同步','Switching data storage while sync is incomplete is dangerous and can lead to order data corruption or loss!'=>'在同步未完成時切換資料儲存空間是很危險的，可能會導致訂單資料損壞或遺失！','Unable to stop synchronization. The link you followed may have expired.'=>'無法停止同步處理。 你關注的連結可能已經過期。','Failed to create FTS index on order item table'=>'無法在訂單項目表格上建立 FTS 索引','Failed to create FTS index on address table'=>'無法在地址表格上建立 FTS 索引','Marketing tactic'=>'行銷策略','Create and use full text search indexes for orders. This feature only works with high-performance order storage.'=>'建立並使用全文搜尋索引來查詢訂單。 此功能僅供高效能訂單儲存空間使用。','HPOS Full text search indexes'=>'HPOS 全文搜尋索引','Arts and crafts'=>'藝術與工藝','Sports and recreation'=>'運動與娛樂','Pickup'=>'取貨','Failed to create FTS index on orders table. This feature is only available when High-performance order storage is enabled.'=>'無法在訂單表格上建立 FTS 索引 唯有在高效能訂單儲存啟用時，才可使用此功能。','You can switch order data storage <strong>only when the posts and orders tables are in sync</strong>. There are currently orders out of sync.'=>'你<strong>只能在文章和訂單表格同步後</strong>，才可以切換訂單資料儲存空間。 目前尚有訂單未同步。','Your subscription for <strong>%1$s</strong> expired. <a href="%3$s">%4$s</a> to continue receiving updates and streamlined support.'=>'你的 <strong>%1$s</strong> 訂閱已到期。請<a href="%3$s">%4$s</a>，如此才能繼續收到更新和簡化又便捷的支援。','Enable auto-renewal'=>'啟用自動續訂','You have <strong>%1$s Woo extension subscriptions</strong> expiring soon. <a href="%2$s">Enable auto-renewal</a> to continue receiving updates and streamlined support.'=>'你有 <strong>%1$s 個 Woo 擴充功能訂閱項目</strong>即將到期。 請<a href="%2$s">啟用自動續訂</a>，如此才能繼續收到更新和簡化又便捷的支援。','One of your subscriptions for <strong>%1$s</strong> expires on %2$s. <a href="%3$s">Enable auto-renewal</a> to continue receiving updates and streamlined support.'=>'你其中一個 <strong>%1$s</strong> 訂閱將於 %2$s到期。 請<a href="%3$s">啟用自動續訂</a>，如此才能繼續收到更新和簡化又便捷的支援。','Your subscription for <strong>%1$s</strong> expires on %2$s. <a href="%3$s">Enable auto-renewal</a> to continue receiving updates and streamlined support.'=>'你的 <strong>%1$s</strong> 訂閱已於 %2$s到期。 請<a href="%3$s">啟用自動續訂</a>，如此才能繼續收到更新和簡化又便捷的支援。','Renew for %1$s'=>'續訂只要 %1$s','This method has been deprecated and will be removed soon. Use Automattic\\WooCommerce\\Utilities\\DiscountsUtil::is_coupon_emails_allowed instead.'=>'此方法已過時，很快就會移除。 請改為使用：Automattic\\WooCommerce\\Utilities\\DiscountsUtil::is_coupon_emails_allowed。','WooCommerce Legacy REST API package'=>'WooCommerce 舊版 REST API 套件','Legacy API v3 (⚠️ NOT AVAILABLE)'=>'舊版 API v3 (⚠️ 無法使用)','Set the action as manual so that the order note registers as "added by user".'=>'手動設定動作，訂單備註即登記為「由使用者新增」。','The Legacy REST API plugin is not installed on this site.'=>'此網站並未安裝舊版 REST API 外掛程式。','The WooCommerce Legacy REST API plugin running on this site.'=>'此網站上執行的是 WooCommerce 舊版 REST API 外掛程式。','Copy for GitHub'=>'複製 GitHub 版','⚠️ The WooCommerce Legacy REST API has been moved to <a target=”_blank” href="%1$s">a dedicated extension</a>. <b><a target=”_blank” href="%2$s">Learn more about this change</a></b>'=>'⚠️ WooCommerce 舊版 REST API 已移至<a target=”_blank” href="%1$s">專屬擴充功能</a>。 <b><a target=”_blank” href="%2$s">深入了解這項變更</a></b>','ℹ️️ The WooCommerce Legacy REST API extension is installed and active.'=>'ℹ️️ WooCommerce 舊版 REST API 擴充功能已安裝並啟用。','The legacy REST API is NOT enabled'=>'舊版 REST API 未啟用','The legacy REST API is enabled'=>'舊版 REST API 已啟用','for %s '=>'價格：%s ','<a href=\'%s\'>More information</a>'=>'<a href=\'%s\'>更多資訊</a>',' Your subscription expires on %1$s, 