merce 的舊版 REST API 與 HPOS <b>不</b>相容。','Track inventory'=>'追蹤庫存','Data in posts table appears to be more recent than in HPOS tables. Compare order data with `wp wc hpos diff %1$d` and use `wp wc hpos backfill %1$d --from=posts --to=hpos` to fix.'=>'文章表格內的資料比 HPOS 表格內的資料還要更新。 將訂單資料與「wp wc hpos diff %1$d」比較，並使用「wp wc hpos backfill %1$d --from=posts --to=hpos」進行修正。','⚠️ The file system connection could not be initialized.'=>'⚠️ 檔案系統連結無法初始化。','You may want to switch to the database for log storage.'=>'你可能會想要切換至記錄儲存空間的資料庫。','⚠️ The file system is not configured for direct writes. This could cause problems for the logger.'=>'⚠️ 檔案系統並未設定為可直接寫入， 這可能會造成記錄器問題。','✅ Ready'=>'✅ 就緒','Cleanup completed for %d order. Review errors above.'=>'已為 %d 筆訂單完成清理作業。 檢閱上述錯誤。','Failed to clean up all orders in a batch. Aborting.'=>'無法以批次方式清理所有訂單。 正在中止。','Template namePage: Coming soon'=>'頁面：即將推出','Your store might be at risk as you are running old versions of WooCommerce plugins.'=>'你若執行舊版 WooCommerce 外掛程式，可能會讓商店面臨風險。','Select your shipping options'=>'選取你的運送選項','
