		','Order attribution information.'=>'訂單歸屬資訊。','Something big is brewing! Our store is in the works and will be launching soon!'=>'有大事要發生了！ 我們正在籌備商店中，很快就會推出！','Attribution'=>'歸屬','Great things are on the horizon'=>'大事即將發生','Name of credit cardCartes Bancaires'=>'Cartes Bancaires','<a id="woo-connect-notice-url" href="%s">Connect your store</a> to WooCommerce.com to get updates and streamlined support for your subscriptions.'=>'<a id="woo-connect-notice-url" href="%s">將你的商店連結</a>至 WooCommerce.com，即可為訂閱取得更新與流暢的支援服務。','There was an error processing your order. Please check for any charges in your payment method and review your <a href="%s">order history</a> before placing the order again.'=>'處理你的訂單時發生錯誤。 請檢查付款方式中的任何費用，並於再次下訂單前，檢閱你的<a href="%s">訂單記錄</a>。',' <a href="%1$s" class="woocommerce-connect-your-store">Connect your store</a> to woocommerce.com to update.'=>' <a href="%1$s" class="woocommerce-connect-your-store">將你的商店連結</a>至 woocommerce.com 以取得更新。','block keywordfields'=>'欄位','block keywordcustom'=>'自訂','block keywordselect'=>'選取','block descriptionThe product custom fields.'=>'商品自訂欄位。','block titleProduct custom fields control'=>'商品自訂欄位控制項目','block descriptionThe product custom fields toggle.'=>'商品自訂欄位切換開關。','block titleProduct custom fields toggle control'=>'商品自訂欄位切換開關控制項目','block descriptionA select field for use in the product editor.'=>'用於商品編輯器的選取欄位。','block titleProduct select field'=>'商品選取欄位','Live'=>'上線','Approving will share credentials with %s. Do not proceed if this looks suspicious in any way.'=>'若你核准，即會與 %s 分享憑證。 若看起來很可疑，請勿繼續。','Plugin installed by %1$s on %2$s.'=>'%1$s 已於 %2$s安裝外掛程式。','Plugin installed by %1$s on %2$s. <a target="_blank" href="%3$s">More information</a>'=>'%1$s 已於 %2$s安裝外掛程式。 <a target="_blank" href="%3$s">更多資訊</a>','Enter an optional note attached to the order confirmation message sent to the shopper.'=>'輸入選填備註，附加至傳送給其他買家的確認訊息。','Post-purchase note'=>'購買後備註','Custom fields'=>'自訂欄位','Show custom fields'=>'顯示自訂欄位','Use global attributes to allow shoppers to filter and search for this product. Use custom attributes to provide detailed product information.'=>'使用全域屬性，允許買家篩選並搜尋此商品。 使用自訂屬性，提供詳細商品資訊。','Custom fields can be used in a variety of ways, such as sharing more detailed product information, showing more input fields, or for internal inventory organization. %1$sRead more about custom fields%2$s'=>'你可透過多種方式運用自訂欄位，例如分享更多詳細商品資訊、顯示更多輸入欄位，或內部庫存整理。 %1$s深入閱讀自訂欄位資訊%2$s','Per your %1$sstore settings%2$s, taxes are not enabled.'=>'根據%1$s商店設定%2$s，未啟用稅金。','Unable to create backup post for order %d.'=>'無法建立訂單「%d」的備份文章。','%s is not a valid order property.'=>'「%s」並非有效的訂單屬性。','%s is an internal meta key. Use --props to set it.'=>'「%s」是內部中繼資料金鑰。 使用「--props」加以設定。','The backup datastore does not support updating orders.'=>'備份資料存放區不支援更新訂單。','New custom field name'=>'新的自訂欄位名稱','Please review the errors above.'=>'請檢閱上方錯誤。','WooCommerce Blocks development mode requires files to be built. From the root directory, run %1$s to ensure your node version is aligned, run %2$s to install dependencies, %3$s to build the files or %4$s to build the files and watch for changes.'=>'需先建立檔案，才能用 WooCommerce 區塊開發模式。 從根目錄執行「%1$s」確保節點版本相符；執行「%2$s」安裝相依性；執行「%3$s」建立檔案；若要建立檔案並監視變更，請執行「%4$s」。','Overriding existing data with an already registered key is not allowed'=>'不允許使用已註冊的金鑰覆寫現有資料','The metaboxhidden_product meta from the user metas.'=>'來自使用者中繼資料的「metaboxhidden_product」中繼資料。','Set up your payment methods and accept credit and debit cards, cash, bank transfers and money from your Mercado Pago account. Offer safe and secure payments with Latin America’s leading processor.'=>'若要從你的 Mercado Pago 帳戶接受信用卡與簽帳金融卡、現金、銀行轉帳付款，請設定付款方式。 透過拉丁美洲的頂尖處理商，提供安全又有保障的付款方式。','Key for the data being registered must be a string'=>'已註冊資料的金鑰必須為字串','Grow your business'=>'拓展業務','Mercado Pago'=>'Mercado Pago','Collect sales tax'=>'收取銷售稅','Add your products'=>'新增商品','It\'s time to celebrate – you\'re ready to launch your store! Woo! Hit the button to preview your store and make it public.'=>'你已經準備好啟動商店了，準備慶祝吧！ Woo！ 點擊按鈕、預覽商店並將商店公開。','Launch your store'=>'啟動你的商店','Get your products shipped'=>'運送商品','Current price is: %s.'=>'目前價格：%s。','Original price was: %s.'=>'原始價格：%s。','Checkout can be customized <a href="%s">in the Editor</a> with your active theme.'=>'可在<a href="%s">編輯器內</a>使用已啟用的佈景主題自訂結帳畫面。','⚠️ WooCommerce attempted to install <a href="%1$s">the Legacy REST API plugin</a> because this site has <a href="%2$s">the Legacy REST API enabled</a> or has <a href="%3$s">legacy webhooks defined</a>, but the installation failed (see error details in <a href="%4$s">the WooCommerce logs</a>). Please install and activate the plugin manually. <a href="%5$s">More information</a>'=>'⚠️ WooCommerce 嘗試安裝<a href="%1$s">舊版 REST API 外掛程式</a>，因為此網站<a href="%2$s">已啟用舊版 REST API</a> 或<a href="%3$s">已定義舊版 webhook</a>，但安裝失敗 (可在 <a href="%4$s">WooCommerce 記錄</a>中查看錯誤詳細資料)。 請手動安裝並啟用外掛程式。 <a href="%5$s">更多資訊</a>','ℹ️ WooCommerce installed and activated <a href="%1$s">the Legacy REST API plugin</a> because this site has <a href="%2$s">the Legacy REST API enabled</a> or has <a href="%3$s">legacy webhooks defined</a>. <a href="%4$s">More information</a>'=>'ℹ️ WooCommerce 已安裝並啟用<a href="%1$s">舊版 REST API 外掛程式</a>，因為此網站<a href="%2$s">已啟用舊版 REST API</a> 或<a href="%3$s">已定義舊版 Webhook</a>。 <a href="%4$s">更多資訊</a>','WooCommerce installed the Legacy REST API plugin but failed to activate it, see context for more details.'=>'WooCommerce 已安裝舊版 REST API 外掛程式但無法啟用，請參閱背景資訊深入了解。','⚠️ WooCommerce installed <a href="%1$s">the Legacy REST API plugin</a> because this site has <a href="%2$s">the Legacy REST API enabled</a> or has <a href="%3$s">legacy webhooks defined</a>, but it failed to activate it (see error details in <a href="%4$s">the WooCommerce logs</a>). Please go to <a href="%5$s">the plugins page</a> and activate it manually. <a href="%6$s">More information</a>'=>'⚠️ WooCommerce 安裝了<a href="%1$s">舊版 REST API 外掛程式</a>，因為此網站<a href="%2$s">已啟用舊版 REST API</a> 或<a href="%3$s">已定義舊版 Webhook</a>，但啟用失敗 (可在 <a href="%4$s">WooCommerce 記錄</a>中檢視錯誤詳細資料)。 請前往<a href="%5$s">外掛程式頁面</a>並手動啟用。 <a href="%6$s">更多資訊</a>','Please enter a valid email at checkout to use coupon code "%s".'=>'若要使用優惠券代碼「%s」，請在結帳時輸入有效的電子郵件地址。','Please enter a valid email to use coupon code "%s".'=>'若要使用優惠券代碼「%s」，請輸入有效的電子郵件地址。','To allow logging, make %s writable.'=>'若要記錄，請將「%s」設為可供寫入。','Local pickup: Set up pickup locations in the <a href="%s">Local pickup settings page</a>.'=>'當地取貨：在<a href="%s">「當地取貨」設定頁面</a>設定取貨地點。','Explore a new enhanced delivery method that allows you to easily offer one or more pickup locations to your customers in the <a href="%s">Local pickup settings page</a>.'=>'探索全新的強化運送方法，讓你在<a href="%s">「當地取貨」設定頁面</a>輕鬆為顧客提供一個或多個取貨地點。','Gathering usage data allows us to tailor your store setup experience, offer more relevant content, and help make WooCommerce better for everyone.'=>'若收集使用情況資料，我們就能量身打造你的商店設定體驗，並提供更相關的內容，為所有使用者提升 WooCommerce。','Please <a href="%1$s">Install the WooCommerce.com Update Manager</a> to continue receiving the updates and streamlined support included in your WooCommerce.com subscriptions. Alternatively, you can <a href="%2$s">download</a> and install it manually.'=>'請<a href="%1$s">安裝 WooCommerce.com Update Manager</a>，繼續接收 WooCommerce.com 訂閱隨附的更新和流暢支援服務。 或者你也可以手動<a href="%2$s">下載</a>並安裝。','Please <a href="%1$s">activate the WooCommerce.com Update Manager</a> to continue receiving the updates and streamlined support included in your WooCommerce.com subscriptions.'=>'請<a href="%1$s">啟用 WooCommerce.com Update Manager</a>，即可繼續接收 WooCommerce.com 訂閱隨附的更新和流暢支援服務。',' Activate WooCommerce.com Update Manager to update.'=>' 只要啟用 WooCommerce.com Update Manager 即可更新。',' <a href="%1$s">Install WooCommerce.com Update Manager</a> to update.'=>' 只要<a href="%1$s">安裝 WooCommerce.com Update Manager</a> 即可更新。','block keywordrich-text'=>'rich-text','block keywordtextarea'=>'多行文字欄位','block descriptionA text-area field for use in the product editor.'=>'用於商品編輯器的多行文字欄位。','block titleProduct textarea block'=>'商品多行文字欄位區塊','block keywordsubsection'=>'子區段','block descriptionThe product subsection description.'=>'商品子區段說明。','block titleProduct subsection description'=>'商品子區段說明','Immediately'=>'立即','Invalid %s provided.'=>'提供的「%s」無效。','Internal server error'=>'內部伺服器錯誤','Sorry, you cannot delete resources.'=>'抱歉，你無法刪除資源。','Sorry, you cannot create resources.'=>'抱歉，你無法建立資源。','Sorry, you cannot view resources.'=>'抱歉，你無法檢視資源。','True to force the creation of a new receipt even if one already exists and has not expired yet.'=>'即使收據已經存在且尚未過期，也可以強制建立新的收據。','Number of days to be added to the current date to get the expiration date.'=>'在目前的日期加上天數，便可產生過期日期。','Expiration date formatted as yyyy-mm-dd.'=>'過期日期的格式為 yyyy-mm-dd。','Expiration date of the receipt, formatted as yyyy-mm-dd.'=>'收據過期日期的格式為 yyyy-mm-dd。','Public url of the receipt.'=>'收據的公開 URL。','Unique identifier of the order.'=>'訂單的唯一識別碼。','Order not found'=>'找不到訂單','Receipt not found'=>'找不到收據','Account Type'=>'帳號類型','AID'=>'輔助','Application Name'=>'應用程式名稱','Payment method'=>'付款方式','Date Paid'=>'付款日期','Amount Paid'=>'付款金額','Discount (%s)'=>'折扣 (%s)','Summary: Order #%d'=>'摘要：訂單 #%d','Receipt'=>'收據','Background process for coupon meta conversion stopped'=>'優惠券 meta 轉換的背景程序已停止','Background process for coupon meta conversion not started, nothing done.'=>'優惠券 meta 轉換的背景程序尚未啟動，未執行任何操作。','Background process for coupon meta conversion started'=>'優惠券 meta 轉換的背景程序已啟動','Background process for coupon meta conversion already started, nothing done.'=>'優惠券 meta 轉換的背景程序已啟動，未執行任何操作。','This will convert <code>coupon_data</code> order item meta entries to simplified <code>coupon_info</code> entries. The conversion will happen overtime in the background (via Action Scheduler). There are currently %d entries that can be converted.'=>'這會將 <code>coupon_data</code> 訂單項目 meta 條目轉換為簡化的 <code>coupon_info</code> 條目。 隨著時間經過，系統會在背景 (經由動作排程器) 執行轉換。 目前有 %d 個條目可轉換。','Convert order coupon data to the simplified format'=>'將訂單優惠券資料轉換為簡化格式','This will stop the background process that converts <code>coupon_data</code> order item meta entries to simplified <code>coupon_info</code> entries. There are currently %d entries that can be converted.'=>'這會停止將 <code>coupon_data</code> 訂單項目 meta 條目轉換為簡化 <code>coupon_info</code> 條目的背景程序。 目前有 %d 個條目可轉換。','Stop converting'=>'停止轉換','Stop converting order coupon data to the simplified format'=>'停止將訂單優惠券資料轉換為簡化格式','This will convert <code>coupon_data</code> order item meta entries to simplified <code>coupon_info</code> entries. The conversion will happen overtime in the background (via Action Scheduler). There are currently no entries to convert.'=>'這會將 <code>coupon_data</code> 訂單項目 meta 條目轉換為簡化的 <code>coupon_info</code> 條目。 隨著時間經過，系統會在背景 (經由動作排程器) 執行轉換。 目前沒有可轉換的條目。','Receipt from %s'=>'「%s」的收據','Start converting'=>'開始轉換','Start converting order coupon data to the simplified format'=>'開始將訂單優惠券資料轉換為簡化格式','%d is not an order or has an invalid order type.'=>'「%d」並非訂單或具有無效的訂單類型。','Order legacy data cleanup process has been started.'=>'已啟動訂單舊版資料清理程序。','No orders in need of cleanup'=>'沒有需要清理的訂單','Order legacy data cleanup has been canceled.'=>'已取消訂單舊版資料清理程序。','Clearing data...'=>'正在清除資料...','Only available when HPOS is authoritative and compatibility mode is disabled.'=>'僅在 HPOS 可供授權且相容模式遭到停用時，才可使用。','Clear data'=>'清除資料','This tool will clear the data from legacy order tables in WooCommerce.'=>'此工具會清除 WooCommerce 中舊版訂單表格的資料。','Clean up order data from legacy tables'=>'清理舊版表格的訂單資料','Order legacy cleanup failed for an entire batch of orders. Aborting cleanup.'=>'整批訂單的訂單舊版清理程序失敗。 中止清理。','Order %1$d legacy data could not be cleaned up during batch process. Error: %2$s'=>'無法在批次處理過程中，清理訂單「%1$d」的舊版資料。 錯誤：%2$s','Directory size: %s'=>'目錄大小：%s','The %s hook has a filter set, so some log files may have different retention settings.'=>'「%s」勾點已設定篩選條件，因此部分記錄檔可能有不同的保留設定。','Order %1$d backfilled from %2$s to %3$s.'=>'訂單「%1$d」從「%2$s」回填至「%3$s」。','An error occurred while backfilling order %1$d from %2$s to %3$s: %4$s'=>'將訂單「%1$d」從「%2$s」回填至「%3$s」時發生錯誤：%4$s','Please use different source (--from) and destination (--to) datastores.'=>'請使用不同的來源 (--from) 與目的地 (--to) 資料存放區。','\'%s\' is not a valid datastore.'=>'「%s」不是有效的資料存放區。','Please provide a valid order ID.'=>'請提供有效的訂單 ID。','Next image'=>'下一張圖片','Previous image'=>'上一張圖片','The image upload failed: "%s", creating the product without image'=>'圖片上傳失敗：「%s」，正在建立沒有圖片的商品','Invalid plugin slug provided in the plugins activated rule.'=>'外掛程式啟用規則所提供的外掛程式代稱無效。','The size of the log directory.'=>'記錄檔目錄的大小。','Minimum severity level.'=>'嚴重程度最小值。','The number of days log entries are retained.'=>'記錄條目的保留天數。','The logging handler class.'=>'記錄處理常式類別。','Logging.'=>'記錄。','Whether the coupon grants free shipping or not.'=>'優惠券是否提供免運。','Discount amount as defined in the coupon (absolute value or a percent, depending on the discount type).'=>'優惠券中所定義的折扣金額 (可設為絕對值或百分比，取決於折扣類型)。','Discount type.'=>'折扣類型。','The total size of the files in the log directory.'=>'記錄檔目錄中的檔案大小總計。','Log directory size'=>'記錄檔目錄大小','The minimum severity level of logs that will be stored.'=>'系統會儲存的記錄嚴重程度最小值。','How many days log entries will be kept before being auto-deleted.'=>'記錄檔條目在系統自動刪除前會保留的天數。','How log entries are being stored.'=>'記錄檔條目的儲存方式。','Handler'=>'處理常式','Is logging enabled?'=>'記錄是否已啟用？','Logging'=>'記錄','Create and save'=>'建立與儲存','Zagora'=>'扎古拉','Youssoufia'=>'優素菲耶','Tan-Tan'=>'坦坦','Tangier-Assilah'=>'丹吉爾-阿西拉','Tiznit'=>'提資尼特','Tinghir'=>'廷吉爾','Tétouan'=>'得土安','Taza'=>'塔沙','Tata'=>'塔塔','Taroudant'=>'塔魯丹特','Taounate'=>'陶納特','Taourirt'=>'陶里爾特','Tarfaya (EH-partial)'=>'塔爾法亞 (部分位於西撒哈拉)','Sidi Youssef Ben Ali'=>'西迪尤賽夫本阿里','Skhirat-Témara'=>'斯基拉特-德馬拉','Sidi Slimane'=>'西迪蘇萊曼','Sidi Kacem'=>'西迪卡塞姆','Sidi Ifni'=>'西迪伊夫尼','Sidi Bennour'=>'西迪本努爾','Settat'=>'塞塔特','Sefrou'=>'賽弗洛','Salé'=>'賽拉','Safi'=>'薩非','Rehamna'=>'賴哈姆納','Rabat'=>'拉巴特','Ouezzane'=>'沃贊','Oujda-Angad'=>'烏季達-安加得','Oued Ed-Dahab'=>'達赫拉-黃金谷地','O