'移除目前排程的動作，刪除過期的暫存檔案。 在「排程過期暫存檔案清理」工具再次執行前，過期檔案不會自動刪除。','Un-schedule expired transient files cleanup'=>'將過期暫存檔案清理作業取消排程','Re-schedule'=>'重新排程','Schedule the action to delete expired transient files for running immediately. Subsequent actions will run once every 24h.'=>'排程動作，刪除立即執行的過期暫存檔案。 後續動作每 24 小時會執行一次。','Remove the currently scheduled action to delete expired transient files, then schedule it again for running immediately. Subsequent actions will run once every 24h.'=>'移除目前已排程的動作，刪除過期的暫存檔案，接著再次排程即可立即執行。 後續動作每 24 小時會執行一次。','Schedule expired transient files cleanup'=>'排程過期暫存檔案的清理作業','Re-schedule expired transient files cleanup'=>'將過期暫存檔案清理作業重新排程','Tip: By suggesting complementary products in the cart using cross-sells, you can significantly increase the average order value.'=>'秘訣：運用交叉銷售在購物車推薦互補的商品，便可大幅提升平均訂單金額。','Medium'=>'中','By suggesting complementary products in the cart using cross-sells, you can significantly increase the average order value. %1$sLearn more about linked products%2$s'=>'運用交叉銷售在購物車推薦互補的商品，便可大幅提升平均訂單金額。 %1$s深入了解連結商品%2$s','Tip: Upsells are products that are extra profitable or better quality or more expensive. Experiment with combinations to boost sales.'=>'秘訣：追加銷售商品的獲利更高、品質更好，或價格更昂貴。 嘗試產品組合，提升銷售額。','Include downloads'=>'包含下載','Linked products'=>'連結商品','Customer Email'=>'顧客的電子郵件','You do not have permission to manage logging settings.'=>'你沒有足夠的權限可管理記錄設定。','Database settings'=>'資料庫設定','Log entries are stored in this database table: %s'=>'記錄條目儲存於此資料庫表格：%s','File system settings'=>'檔案系統設定','⚠️ This directory does not appear to be writable.'=>'⚠️ 此目錄不提供寫入。','Log files are stored in this directory: %s'=>'記錄檔案儲存於此目錄：%s','Unable to start synchronization. The link you followed may have expired.'=>'無法開始啟動同步處理。 你關注的連結可能已經過期。','Upsells are typically products that are extra profitable or better quality or more expensive. Experiment with combinations to boost sales. %1$sLearn more about linked products%2$s'=>'追加銷售商品通常獲利更高、品質更好，或價格更昂貴。 嘗試產品組合，提升銷售額。 %1$s深入了解連結商品%2$s','This sets the minimum severity level of logs that will be stored. Lower severity levels will be ignored. "None" means all logs will be stored.'=>'這設定了會儲存的記錄嚴重程度最小值。 系統會忽略較低的嚴重程度。 「沒有」代表系統會儲存所有記錄。','Level threshold'=>'程度門檻','This setting cannot be changed here because it is defined in the %1$s constant, probably in your %2$s file.'=>'由於此設定是由 %1$s 常數定義的 (可能位於 %2$s 檔案中)，所以在此處無法變更。','This sets how many days log entries will be kept before being auto-deleted.'=>'這會設定記錄條目由系統自動刪除前，會保留的天數。','Retention period'=>'保留期間','This setting cannot be changed here because it is being set by a filter on the %s hook.'=>'此設定無法在此變更，因為是由 %s 勾點中的篩選條件進行設定。','This determines where log entries are saved.'=>'這會決定系統儲存記錄條目的位置。','Log storage'=>'記錄儲存空間','This setting cannot be changed here because it is defined in the %s constant.'=>'由於此設定是由 %s 常數定義的，所以在此處無法變更。','Note that if this setting is changed, any log entries that have already been recorded will remain stored in their current location, but will not migrate.'=>'請注意，若設定已變更，則任何已記錄的記錄條目將繼續儲存於目前的位置，不會移轉至他處。','Database (not recommended on live sites)'=>'資料庫 (不建議用於已上線的網站)','File system (default)'=>'檔案系統 (預設)','Logger'=>'記錄器','Logs settings'=>'記錄設定','Logging is disabled. It can be enabled in <a href="%s">Logs Settings</a>.'=>'記錄已停用。 可以在<a href="%s">記錄設定</a>中啟用。','%1$s log file from source %2$s was deleted.'=>'來源 %2$s 有 %1$s 個記錄檔案已刪除。','Differences found for order %d:'=>'找到訂單 %d 的差異處：','No differences found.'=>'沒有找到差異。','An error occurred while computing a diff for order %1$d: %2$s'=>'運算訂單 %1$d 的差異時出現錯誤：%2$s','Orders subject to cleanup: %d'=>'訂單需清理：%d','Unsynced orders: %d'=>'未同步的訂單：%d','Compatibility mode enabled?: %s'=>'已啟用相容模式？：%s','HPOS enabled?: %s'=>'已啟用 HPOS？：%s','A link to a product sold on a different website, e.g. brand collab.'=>'在不同網站販售的商品的連結，如品牌合作。','Affiliate product'=>'附屬商品','A set of products that go well together, e.g. camera kit.'=>'適合互相搭配的一系列商品，如相機組。','A single physical or virtual product, e.g. a t-shirt or an eBook.'=>'單一的實體或虛擬商品，如 T 恤或電子書。','Boost international sales and save on FX fees. Accept 60+ local payment methods including Apple Pay and Google Pay.'=>'提高國際銷量並節省國外刷卡手續費。 接受超過 60 種當地付款方式，包含 Apple Pay 和 Google Pay。','Airwallex Payments'=>'Airwallex 付款方式','Coupons for groups. Provides the option to have coupons that are restricted to group members or roles. Works with the free Groups plugin.'=>'群組優惠券。 提供僅限於群組成員或角色使用的優惠券選項。 運用免費的群組外掛程式運作。','Give away a free item to any customer with the coupon code.'=>'只要顧客擁有優惠券代碼，即可兌換免費商品。','Create "store credit" coupons for customers which are redeemable at checkout.'=>'建立結帳時可供顧客兌換的「商店點數」優惠券。','Create a unique URL that applies a discount and optionally adds one or more products to the customer\'s cart.'=>'建立唯一的 URL，不只可使用折扣，還可視需求新增一或多項商品至顧客的購物車。','Powerful, "all in one" solution for gift certificates, store credits, discount coupons and vouchers.'=>'強大的「全方位」解決方案，一手包辦禮券、商店點數、折扣優惠券和抵用券。','Generate dynamic personalized coupons for your customers that increase purchase rates.'=>'為顧客產生靈活的個人版優惠券，刺激購買率。','Sync your website\'s data like contacts, products, and orders over Salesforce CRM with Salesforce Integration for WooCommerce.'=>'運用 WooCommerce 的 Salesforce 整合工具，同步處理聯絡資訊、商品資訊和 Salesforce CRM 上的訂單等網站資料。','Integrate your WooCommerce store with 5000+ cloud apps and services today. Trusted by 11,000+ users.'=>'WooCommerce 商店現可整合超過 5000 個雲端應用程式和服務。 深受超過 11,000 位使用者信賴。','Harness data from WooCommerce to grow your business. Manage leads, customers, and segments, through automation, quotes, invoicing, billing, and email marketing. Power up your store with CRM.'=>'善用 WooCommerce 的資料來拓展業務。 運用自動化作業、報價、發票、帳單和電子郵件行銷等功能，管理潛在客戶、顧客和市場區隔。 透過 CRM 讓商店更強大。','Turn your product images into stunning videos that engage and convert audiences - no video experience required.'=>'將商品圖片變成引人注目的影片，藉此增加互動並轉換受眾，無須任何影片製作經驗亦可。','Collect and showcase verified reviews that consumers trust.'=>'收集並展示可供顧客信賴的已驗證評論。','Delight customers and boost organic sales with a special WooCommerce birthday email (and coupon!) on their special day.'=>'在顧客的生日透過 WooCommerce 的電子郵件生日賀卡 (暨優惠券！) 取悅顧客，刺激有機銷售表現。','Boost your organic sales by adding a customer referral program to your WooCommerce store.'=>'將顧客推薦計畫加入 WooCommerce 商店，刺激有機銷售表現。','Convert and retain customers with automated marketing that does the hard work for you.'=>'讓自動行銷為你代勞苦差事，成功轉換和保留顧客。','Send targeted campaigns, recover abandoned carts and more with Mailchimp.'=>'有了 Mailchimp，便可傳送目標明確的行銷活動通知，以及協助恢復購買購物車未結商品等等。','Create advertising campaigns and reach one billion global users with TikTok for WooCommerce.'=>'使用 TikTok for WooCommerce 建立廣告活動並觸及 10 億名全球使用者。','Grow your business on Pinterest! Use this official plugin to allow shoppers to Pin products while browsing your store, track conversions, and advertise on Pinterest.'=>'在 Pinterest 拓展業務！ 使用官方外掛程式，讓購物者在瀏覽商店時可以釘選商品，並且讓你追蹤轉換和在 Pinterest 上刊登廣告。','CRM'=>'CRM','Conversion'=>'轉換','Automations'=>'自動化作業','Sales channels'=>'銷售通路','Override the "woocommerce_date_type" option that is used for the database date field considered for revenue reports.'=>'覆寫「woocommerce_date_type」選項，因為已用於收益報告會納入考量的資料庫日期欄位。','Sorry, you cannot create dummy products.'=>'很抱歉，你無法建立示範商品。','Sales of the marketing campaign.'=>'行銷活動銷售額。','Limit result set to specific amount of suggested products.'=>'限制結果設定為建議商品的特定數量。','Limit result set to specific product tag ids.'=>'限制結果設定為特定商品標籤 ID。','Limit result set to specific product categorie ids.'=>'限制結果設定為特定商品類別 ID。','Invalid layout template ID.'=>'無效的版面配置範本 ID。','Area to get templates for.'=>'取得範本的區域。','The downloadable file %s cannot be used as it does not exist on the server, or is not located within an approved directory. Please contact a site administrator for help. %2$sLearn more.%3$s'=>'無法使用「%s」下載檔案，因為在伺服器中找不到檔案，或並非位於核准的目錄中。 請聯絡網站管理員尋求協助。 %2$s深入了解。%3$s','Could not start the installation process. Reason: '=>'無法啟動安裝程序。 原因： ','block descriptionEnable customers to filter the product collection by rating.'=>'讓顧客依評分篩選產品系列。','block descriptionThe prod