y button'=>'購買按鈕','This product has options, such as size or color. You can manage each variation\'s images, downloads, and other details individually.'=>'此產品提供不同選項，例如尺寸或顏色。 你可以分別管理每個款式的圖片、下載和其他詳細資訊。','This variation will not trigger your customer\'s shipping calculator in cart or at checkout. This product also won\'t require your customers to enter their shipping details at checkout. <a href="https://woocommerce.com/document/managing-products/#adding-a-virtual-product" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Read more about virtual products</a>.'=>'此款式不會在購物車中或結帳時觸發顧客的運費計算機。 此商品也不會在顧客結帳時要求其輸入配送詳細資料。 <a href="https://woocommerce.com/document/managing-products/#adding-a-virtual-product" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">進一步了解虛擬商品</a>。','%s log file deleted.'=>'已刪除 %s 個記錄檔。','You do not have permission to manage log files.'=>'你沒有足夠的權限管理記錄檔案。','Current'=>'目前','File rotations:'=>'檔案旋轉：','Viewing log file %s'=>'檢視記錄檔 %s','Delete this log file permanently?'=>'是否要永久刪除此記錄檔？','Return to the file list.'=>'返回檔案清單。','Browse log files'=>'瀏覽記錄檔','Select the %1$s log file for %2$s'=>'選取 %2$s 的 %1$s 記錄檔','File size'=>'檔案大小','Date modified'=>'修改日期','Filter by log source'=>'依記錄來源篩選','No log files found.'=>'找不到記錄檔。','This file does not exist.'=>'此檔案不存在。','Could not access the log file directory.'=>'無法存取記錄檔目錄。','%1$s was called with an invalid event type "%2$s".'=>'%1$s 受到無效事件類型「%2$s」的呼叫。','Caught exception while enqueuing action "%1$s": %2$s'=>'將動作「%1$s」加入佇列時發現例外：%2$s','e.g. Local pickup'=>'例如，自行取貨','Customers will need to spend this amount to get free shipping.'=>'消費者獲得免運的最低消費金額。','A minimum order amount AND coupon'=>'最小訂購金額與優惠券','A minimum order amount OR coupon'=>'最小訂購金額或優惠券','No requirement'=>'無條件','Free shipping requires'=>'如要享有免運的話需要','e.g. Free shipping'=>'例如，免運費','Please enter a valid number.'=>'請輸入有效的數字。','e.g. Standard national'=>'例如，國內標準','Your customers will see the name of this shipping method during checkout.'=>'顧客會於結帳時看見此配送方式的名稱。','advanced costs'=>'進階費用','Charge a flat rate per