ovided as value.'=>'提供的值為不支援的引數類型。','Invalid password. Generate a new one from %s.'=>'密碼無效。 從 %s 產生新密碼。','Connection password:'=>'連結密碼：','If you don\'t have an application password (not your account password), generate a password from %s'=>'如果你還沒有應用程式密碼 (非帳號密碼)，請從 %s 產生','Your store is already connected.'=>'你的商店已完成連結。','Customers can still save the file to their device, but by default file will be opened instead of being downloaded (does not work with redirects).'=>'顧客仍然可以將檔案儲存到自己的裝置上，但檔案會根據預設開啟，而非直接下載 (不適用重新導向)。','Open downloadable files in the browser, instead of saving them to the device.'=>'在瀏覽器開啟可供下載的檔案，而非儲存到裝置中。','Open in browser'=>'在瀏覽器中開啟','Summarize this product in 1-2 short sentences. We’ll show it at the top of the page.'=>'以 1 到 2 個簡短句子摘要說明這項商品。 我們會將它顯示在頁面頂端。','Empty Mini-Cart Message'=>'迷你購物車中空無一物的訊息','Your store is not connected to WooCommerce.com. Run `wp wc com connect` command.'=>'你的商店並未連結到 WooCommerce.com。 執行「wp wc com connect」命令。','Are you sure you want to disconnect your store from WooCommerce.com?'=>'你確定要取消商店與 WooCommerce.com 的連結？','Describe this product. What makes it unique? What are its most important features?'=>'請描述這項商品。 它有哪些獨特之處？ 它最重要的功能是什麼？','Product types define available product details and attributes, such as downloadable files and variations. They’re also used for analytics and inventory management.'=>'商品類型決定了可用的商品詳細資訊和屬性，例如可下載的檔案和款式。 類型也會用於分析及庫存管理。','<b>Variable –</b> a product with variations, each of which may have a different SKU, price, stock option, etc. For example, a t-shirt available in different colors and/or sizes.'=>'<b>可變 –</b> 擁有其他款式的商品，每種款式都可能有不同的 SKU、價格、庫存選項等。 舉例來說，一件 T 恤可能會有不同的顏色和/或尺寸。','<b>External or Affiliate –</b> one that you list and describe on your website but is sold elsewhere.'=>'<b>外部或聯盟 –</b> 商品列在你的網站上並提供說明，但透過其他管道銷售。','<b>Grouped –</b> a collection of related products that can be purchased individually and only consist of simple products. For example, a set of six drinking glasses.'=>'<b>群組 –</b> 一系列相關商品，可分別購買，當中僅包含簡單的商品。 例如，一組六支水杯。','<b>Simple –</b> covers the vast majority of any products you may sell. Simple products are shipped and have no options. For example, a book.'=>'<b>簡單 –</b> 包含大多數你可能販售的任何商品。 簡單商品可直接出貨，沒有其他選項。 例如圖書。','Sofia District'=>'索菲亞區','block descriptionDisplay products from your store in a grid layout.'=>'以格狀版面顯示商店的商品。','block titleAll Products'=>'所有商品','block descriptionDisplay a grid of products from your selected categories.'=>'顯示所選分類的商品方格。','block titleProducts by Category'=>'依分類排列商品','block descriptionShow all product categories as a list or dropdown.'=>'以清單或下拉式選單顯示所有商品分類。','block titleProduct Categories List'=>'商品分類清單','block descriptionDisplay a grid of your all-time best selling products.'=>'顯示歷來最暢銷商品的方格。','block titleBest Selling Products'=>'最暢銷商品','You cannot edit this item because it is in the Trash. Please restore it and try again.'=>'你無法編輯此項目，因為它在垃圾桶中。 請將它恢復並再試一次。','This info will be displayed on the product page, category pages, social media, and search results.'=>'這些資訊會在商品頁面、分類頁面、社交媒體和搜尋結果中顯示。','Product Details'=>'商品詳細資料','Postcode / ZIP:'=>'郵遞區號：','City:'=>'城市：','Country / region'=>'國家/地區','Thumbnail image'=>'縮圖圖片','Can not re-use table alias "%s" in OrdersTableQuery.'=>'無法在 OrdersTableQuery 中重複使用表格別名「%s」。','%s can not be used as a table alias in OrdersTableQuery'=>'%s 無法用作 OrdersTableQuery 中的表格別名','Invalid order IDs in call to read_multiple()'=>'呼叫 read_multiple() 的訂單 ID 無效','List products and create ads on Facebook and Instagram.'=>'製作商品清單並在 Facebook 和 Instagram 上建立廣告。','You attempted to edit an order that does not exist. Perhaps it was deleted?'=>'你嘗試編輯不存在的訂單。 或許它已經被刪除了？','Key'=>'金鑰','Add Custom Field'=>'新增自訂欄位','Enter new'=>'輸入新欄位','Value'=>'值','Add New Custom Field:'=>'新增自訂欄位：','Custom fields can be used to add extra metadata to an order that you can %1$suse in your theme%2$s.'=>'自訂欄位可用於為訂單新增額外的中繼資料，而你可%1$s在你的佈景主題中使用%2$s此類訂單。','Custom Fields'=>'自訂欄位','Invalid table id: %s.'=>'無效表格 ID: %s。','With WooPayments, you can se