n?'=>'每日 cron 工作為啟用狀態嗎？下次執行時間為何？','Daily Cron'=>'每日 Cron','Which features are disabled?'=>'哪些功能已停用？','Disabled Features'=>'已停用的功能','Which features are enabled?'=>'哪些功能已啟用？','Enabled Features'=>'已啟用的功能','This section shows details of WC Admin.'=>'此區段會顯示 WC 管理員的詳細資料。','Admin'=>'管理員','Grow your online sales by promoting your products on TikTok to over one billion monthly active users around the world.'=>'在 TikTok 上向全球每月超過 10 億名活躍使用者宣傳你的產品，藉此提升線上銷售額。','TikTok for WooCommerce'=>'TikTok for WooCommerce','There is %1$d order to be verified.'=>'%1$d 筆訂單待驗證。','Verification completed.'=>'驗證完成。','Infinite loop detected, aborting. No errors found.'=>'偵測到無限迴圈，正在中止。 沒有找到任何錯誤。','Beginning verification for batch #%1$d (%2$d orders/batch).'=>'正在開始驗證第 %1$d 批次 (每批次 %2$d 筆訂單)。','There are no orders to verify, aborting.'=>'沒有待驗證的訂單，正在中止。','Beginning batch #%1$d (%2$d orders/batch).'=>'正在開始第 %1$d 批次 (每批次 %2$d 筆訂單)。','Custom order table usage is not enabled. If you are testing, you can enable it by following the testing instructions in %s'=>'自訂訂單表格使用功能並未啟用。 若你正在測試，可按照 %s 中的測試指示啟用此功能。','Admin menu nameHome'=>'首頁','Whether an order needs processing before it can be completed.'=>'訂單是否需處理才能完成。','Whether an order needs payment, based on status and order total.'=>'訂單是否需要付款 (視狀態和訂單總額而定)。','Whether an order can be edited.'=>'訂單是否可以編輯。','Properties of the main product image.'=>'主要產品圖片的內容。','Failed to initialise WC_Filesystem API while trying to update the MaxMind Geolocation database.'=>'嘗試更新 MaxMind 地理位置資料庫時，無法初始化 WC_Filesystem API。','PIN Code'=>'PIN 碼','String processors must be an array of valid callbacks.'=>'字串處理器必須是有效回呼的陣列。','%1$d order was verified in %2$d seconds.'=>'已在 %2$d 秒內驗證 %1$d 筆訂單。','Batch %1$d (%2$d orders) completed in %3$d seconds.'=>'已於 %3$d 秒內完成第 %1$d 批次 (%2$d 筆訂單)。','There are no orders to sync, aborting.'=>'沒有要同步的訂單，正在中止。','There is %1$d order to be synced.'=>'有 %1$d 筆訂單要同步。','%1$d order was synced in %2$d seconds.'=>'已在 %2$d 秒內同步 %1$d 筆訂單。','block descriptionShows cart ite