led.'=>'已停用 %d 個核准的目錄 URL。','%d approved directory URL enabled.'=>'已啟用 %d 個核准的目錄 URL。','%d approved directory URL deleted.'=>'已刪除 %d 個核准的目錄 URL。','Approved product download directoriesDirectory URL'=>'目錄 URL','Add New Approved Directory'=>'新增核准的目錄','Edit Approved Directory'=>'編輯核准的目錄','Approved product download directoriesThe provided ID was invalid.'=>'提供的 ID 無效。','Approved Download Directories'=>'核准的下載目錄','Approved product download directoriesStart Enforcing Rules'=>'開始執行規則','Approved product download directoriesStop Enforcing Rules'=>'停止執行規則','Approved Directory URLsSearch'=>'搜尋','Approved download directories'=>'核准的下載目錄','Approved product download directoriesDisable All'=>'取消全部','Approved product download directoriesEnable All'=>'啟用全部','Disable rule'=>'停用規則','Enable rule'=>'啟用規則','Product downloads listDelete permanently'=>'永久刪除','Product downloads listEdit'=>'編輯','Approved product download directoriesEnabled'=>'已啟用','Approved product download directoriesURL'=>'URL','Approved product download directory viewsDisabled <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'已停用 <span class="count">(%s)</span>','Approved product download directory viewsEnabled <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'已啟用 <span class="count">(%s)</span>','Approved product download directory viewsAll <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'全部 <span class="count">(%s)</span>','No approved directory URLs found.'=>'找不到已核准的目錄 URL。','You do not have permission to modify the list of approved directories for product downloads.'=>'你沒有權限修正產品下載項目的已核准目錄清單。','Approved Download Directories sync: scan has been cancelled.'=>'核准的下載目錄同步：已取消掃瞄作業。','The Approved Product Download Directories list is currently being synchronized with the product catalog (%d%% complete). If you need to, you can cancel it.'=>'核准的產品下載目錄清單目前正在同步產品目錄 (完成進度：%d%%)。 如果需要，您可以取消同步。','Cancel synchronization of approved directories'=>'取消同步核准的目錄','Removes all existing entries from the Approved Product Download Directories list.'=>'從核准的產品下載目錄清單中移除所有現有項目