tocked.'=>'若為 true，退款商品會重新補貨。','Shipping Phone Number'=>'送貨電話號碼','Billing Phone Number'=>'帳單電話號碼','Page titleRefund and Returns Policy'=>'退款和退貨政策','Page slugrefund_returns'=>'refund_returns','%1$s at %2$s %3$s'=>'%1$s 於 %2$s %3$s','Edit page'=>'編輯頁面','We have created a sample draft Refund and Returns Policy page for you. Please have a look and update it to fit your store.'=>'我們已為你建立退款和退貨政策的範例草稿頁面。 請查看該頁面並視貴店需求加以更新。','Setup a Refund and Returns Policy page to boost your store\'s credibility.'=>'設定退款和退貨政策頁面，提高商店可信度。','%1$s could not be served using the Force Download method. A redirect will be used instead.'=>'無法使用「強制下載」處理 %1$s。  將改用重新導向。','%1$s could not be served using the X-Accel-Redirect/X-Sendfile method. A Force Download will be used instead.'=>'無法使用「X-Accel-Redirect/X-Sendfile」處理 %1$s。 將改用「強制下載」。','Limit result set to products that are low or out of stock. (Deprecated)'=>'將結果集限定在庫存不足或沒有庫存的產品。 (已過時)','If the "Force Downloads" or "X-Accel-Redirect/X-Sendfile" download method is selected but does not work, the system will use the "Redirect" method as a last resort. <a href="%1$s">See this guide</a> for more details.'=>'如果選取「強制下載」或「X-Accel-Redirect/X-Sendfile」下載方式但無效，系統最終會採用「重新導向」。 如需詳細資訊，<a href="%1$s">請參閱本指南</a>。','Allow using redirect mode (insecure) as a last resort'=>'允許使用重新導向模式 (不安全) 做為最後手段','Set your store location and where you\'ll ship to.'=>'設定你的商店地點和送貨目的地。','Choose payment providers and enable payment methods at checkout.'=>'在結帳時選擇支付服務提供者並啟用付款方式。','You\'re only one step away from getting paid. Verify your business details to start managing transactions with WooPayments.'=>'只要再完成一個步驟，就能開始收款。 驗證企業詳細資訊，就能開始使用 WooPayments 管理交易。','Start by adding the first product to your store. You can add your products manually, via CSV, or import them from another service.'=>'第一步，在商店新增第一項產品。 你可以手動新增產品、透過 CSV 新增，或從其他服務匯入產品。','Your store address is required to set the origin country for shipping, currencies, and payment options.'=>'你需要提供商店地址才能為運送、貨幣和付款選項設定原產國家/地區。','Set your store location and configure tax rate settings.'=>'設定你的商店地點及稅率設定。','Grow your store'=>'讓你的商店成長茁壯','The rate at which tax is applied.'=>'徵收稅金的稅率。','Notes are unavailable because the "admin-note" data store cannot be loaded.'=>'無法載入「管理員備註」資料存放區，因此無法查看備註。','Get backups'=>'取得備份','Store downtime means lost sales. One-click restores get you back online quickly if something goes wrong.'=>'網站無法運作，就會錯失商機。 若發生錯誤，按一下還原就能立即重新上線。','Protect your WooCommerce Store with Jetpack Backup.'=>'使用 Jetpack 備份，保護你的 WooCommerce 商店。','Mollie'=>'Mollie','The Payfast extension for WooCommerce enables you to accept payments by Credit Card and EFT via one of South Africa’s most popular payment gateways. No setup fees or monthly subscription costs. Selecting this extension will configure your store to use South African rands as the selected currency.'=>'使用 WooCommerce 的 PayFast 擴充功能，便能透過南非最受歡迎的付款閘道之一，使用信用卡和 EFT 收款。 無需支付設定費或訂閱月費。 若選擇此擴充功能，你的商店會設為使用南非蘭特作為所選貨幣。','Number of variation items sold.'=>'售出款式項目數量。','Variations Sold'=>'售出的款式','Number of product items sold.'=>'售出產品項目數量。','Source of note.'=>'備註來源。','Data store:'=>'資料存放區：','This section shows details of Action Scheduler.'=>'此區段顯示動作排程器的詳細資料。','Products by Rating list'=>'好評商品清單','Recently Viewed Products list'=>'近期瀏覽商品清單','Change status to cancelled'=>'變更狀態為已取消','Download %d ID'=>'下載 %d ID','Products sold'=>'售出的商品','Things to do next'=>'後續步驟','Manage transactions without leaving your WordPress Dashboard. Only with WooPayments.'=>'不用離開 WordPress 儀表板就能管理交易。 一切收款便利功能，只在 WooPayments。','Create and send purchase follow-up emails, newsletters, and promotional campaigns straight from your dashboard.'=>'直接從控制台建立並傳送購買後續追蹤電子郵件、電子報和行銷活動。','A link to a product.'=>'產品的連結。','Product Link'=>'產品連結','A link to a product tag.'=>'產品標籤的連結。','Product Tag Link'=>'產品標籤連結','A link to a product category.'=>'產品類別的連結。','Product Category Link'=>'產品類別連結','Invalid path provided.'=>'提供的路徑無效。','To ensure your store&rsquo;s notifications arrive in your and your customers&rsquo; inboxes, we recommend connecting your email address to your domain and setting up a dedicated SMTP server. If something doesn&rsquo;t seem to be sending correctly, install the <a href="%1$s">WP Mail Logging Plugin</a> or check the <a href="%2$s">Email FAQ page</a>.'=>'為確保貴商店的通知送達你本人和顧客的收件匣，建議你連結電子郵件地址與網域，並設定專用的 SMTP 伺服器。 如有內容未正確傳送，請安裝 <a href="%1$s">WP 郵件記錄外掛程式</a>或查看<a href="%2$s">電子郵件常見問題頁面</a>。','How easy was it to add a product tag?'=>'新增產品標籤有多簡單？','Filling in progress (%d)'=>'填寫中 (%d)','Product attributes lookup table data is regenerating'=>'正在重新產生產品屬性查詢表資料','Regenerate the product attributes lookup table'=>'重新產生產品屬性查詢表','Delta Amacuro'=>'阿馬庫羅三角洲','Federal Dependencies'=>'聯邦屬地','Zulia'=>'蘇利亞','Yaracuy'=>'亞拉奎','Trujillo'=>'特魯希略','Táchira'=>'塔奇拉','Sucre'=>'蘇克雷','Portuguesa'=>'葡萄牙薩','Nueva Esparta'=>'新埃斯帕塔','Monagas'=>'莫納加斯','Miranda'=>'米蘭達','Mérida'=>'梅里達','Lara'=>'拉臘','Guárico'=>'瓜里科','Falcón'=>'法爾孔市','Cojedes'=>'科赫德斯','Carabobo'=>'卡拉博博','Bolívar'=>'玻利瓦爾','Barinas'=>'巴里納斯','Aragua'=>'阿拉瓜','Apure'=>'阿普雷','Anzoátegui'=>'安索阿德吉','Capital'=>'首都','This tool will regenerate the product attributes lookup table data from existing product(s) data. This process may take a while.'=>'此工具將從現有產品資料重新產生產品屬性查詢表資料。  此程序可能須花費一段時間。','MailPoet'=>'MailPoet','Paystack helps African merchants accept one-time and recurring payments online with a modern, safe, and secure payment gateway.'=>'Paystack 利用安全可靠的現代化支付閘道，幫助非洲商家在線上接受一次性和定期付款。','Paystack'=>'Paystack','How easy was it to add a product attribute?'=>'新增產品屬性有多簡單？','How easy was it to add product category?'=>'新增產品分類有多簡單？','How easy was it to use search?'=>'使用搜尋功能有多簡單？','%s connected successfully'=>'%s 已成功連結','Hi there,'=>'你好：','%s (optional)'=>'%s (選填)','Enable PayU’s exclusive plugin for WooCommerce to start accepting payments in 100+ payment methods available in India including credit cards, debit cards, UPI, & more!'=>'啟用 PayU 的 WooCommerce 專屬外掛程式，開始收取印度超過 100 種付款方式的款項，包括信用卡、簽帳金融卡和 UPI 等！','PayU for WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce 專屬 