er.'=>'如果為 True，每筆訂單限購一個此商品。','True if backorders are allowed past stock availability.'=>'如果允許無庫存可下單，則為 True。','Line subtotal tax.'=>'品項稅金小計。','Word count type. Do not translate!words'=>'characters_excluding_spaces','The ID of the package the shipping rates belong to.'=>'運費所屬包裹 ID。','Name of the package.'=>'包裹名稱。','Shipping destination address.'=>'送貨目的地地址。','List of cart items the returned shipping rates apply to.'=>'傳回運費適用的購物車商品清單。','Name of the item.'=>'商品名稱。','Quantity of the item in the current package.'=>'目前包裹中此商品的數量。','List of shipping rates.'=>'運費清單。','ID of the shipping rate.'=>'運費 ID。','Name of the shipping rate, e.g. Express shipping.'=>'運費名稱，例如：快捷送貨。','Description of the shipping rate, e.g. Dispatched via USPS.'=>'運費說明，例如：透過 USPS 派送。','Delivery time estimate text, e.g. 3-5 business days.'=>'預計送達時間文字，例如：3 到 5 個工作日。','Price of this shipping rate using the smallest unit of the currency.'=>'此運費金額 (依貨幣最小單位提供)。','ID of the shipping method that provided the rate.'=>'運費送貨方式 ID。','Decimal separator for the currency which can be used to format returned prices.'=>'貨幣的小數點，可用於格式化傳回的價格。','An array of data being returned from the payment gateway.'=>'付款閘道傳回的資料陣列。','Status of the payment returned by the gateway. One of success, pending, failure, error.'=>'閘道傳回的付款狀態。 成功、待處理、失敗或錯誤。','True if the cart needs payment. False for carts with only free products and no shipping costs.'=>'如果購物車商品需要付款，則為 True。 如果購物車內只有免費商品且免運費，則為 False。','Current set shipping address for the customer.'=>'顧客目前設定的送貨地址。','List of available shipping rates for the cart.'=>'購物車可用的運費清單。','List of applied cart coupons.'=>'已用於購物車的優惠券清單。','A URL to redirect the customer after checkout. This could be, for example, a link to the payment processors website.'=>'結帳後重新導向顧客的 URL， 可以是付款處理方網站的連結。','Cart total amounts provided using the smallest unit of the currency.'=>'購物車總金額 (依貨幣最小單位提供)。','Total price of items in the cart.'=>'購物車商品總金額。','Total tax on items in the cart.'=>'購物車商品總稅額。','Total price of any applied fees.'