ck on the store setup experience so we can improve it in the future.'=>'既然你選擇與我們合作，我們的目標是確保提供合適的工具來滿足你的需求。 我們期待收到你對商店設定的意見回饋，以便我們之後進行改善。','Watch tutorial'=>'觀看教學課程','Changing eCommerce platforms might seem like a big hurdle to overcome, but it is easier than you might think to move your products, customers, and orders to WooCommerce. This article will help you with going through this process.'=>'更換電子商務平台似乎困難重重，但將商品、顧客和訂單轉移到 WooCommerce 比想像中容易許多。 本文將協助你完成轉移程序。','WooCommerce Subscriptions allows you to introduce a variety of subscriptions for physical or virtual products and services. Create product-of-the-month clubs, weekly service subscriptions or even yearly software billing packages. Add sign-up fees, offer free trials, or set expiration periods.'=>'WooCommerce 訂閱可讓你推出各種實體或虛擬商品和服務的訂閱。 建立每月商品俱樂部、每週服務訂閱，甚至是年度軟體收費方案。 新增註冊費、提供免費試用，或設定有效期限。','Do you want to migrate from Shopify to WooCommerce?'=>'要從 Shopify 移轉到 WooCommerce 嗎？','Taita-Taveta'=>'泰塔塔維塔郡','Tana River'=>'塔納河','Tharaka-Nithi'=>'薩拉卡尼蒂郡','Trans Nzoia'=>'特蘭斯-恩佐亞郡','Turkana'=>'圖爾卡納郡','Uasin Gishu'=>'瓦辛基蘇郡','Vihiga'=>'韋希加郡','Wajir'=>'瓦吉爾','West Pokot'=>'西波克特郡','One or more tables required for WooCommerce to function are missing, some features may not work as expected. Missing tables: %1$s.'=>'缺少一或多個 WooCommerce 所需資料表，某些功能可能無法正常運作。 缺少資料表：%1$s。','Bomet'=>'博美特','Baringo'=>'巴林戈郡','Elgeyo-Marakwet'=>'埃爾格約-馬拉奎特郡','Bungoma'=>'奔戈馬','Garissa'=>'加里薩','Embu'=>'恩布','Isiolo'=>'伊西奧洛','Homa Bay'=>'霍馬灣','Mandera'=>'曼德拉','Makueni'=>'馬瓜尼郡','Machakos'=>'馬查科斯','Lamu'=>'拉穆鎮','Laikipia'=>'萊基皮亞郡','Kwale'=>'夸勒郡','Nyeri'=>'尼耶利','Nyandarua'=>'年達魯阿郡','Nyamira'=>'尼亞米拉郡','Narok'=>'納羅克','Nandi'=>'南迪郡','Nakuru'=>'納庫魯','Nairobi County'=>'內羅畢郡','Kajiado'=>'卡耶亞多郡','Kakamega'=>'卡卡梅加','Kericho'=>'凱里喬','Kiambu'=>'基安布郡','Kilifi'=>'基利菲縣','Kirinyaga'=>'基里尼亞加郡','Kisii'=>'基西','Kitui'=>'基圖伊','Kisumu'=>'基蘇木','Migori'=>'米戈利','Meru'=>'梅魯','Murang’a'=>'穆拉格縣','Mombasa'=>'蒙巴薩','Marsabit'=>'馬薩比特','Siaya'=>'夏亞郡','Samburu'=>'桑布盧郡','Features'=>'功能','Start using ne