 和 WooCommerce Shipping & Tax 時發生問題。 請再試一次。','We noticed that there was a problem during the Jetpack and WooCommerce Shipping & Tax install. Please try again and enjoy all the advantages of having the plugins connected to your store! Sorry for the inconvenience. The "Jetpack" and "WooCommerce Shipping & Tax" plugins will be installed & activated for free.'=>'我們發現安裝 Jetpack 和 WooCommerce Shipping & Tax 時發生問題。 請再試一次，然後享受將外掛程式連結至商店所帶來的一切優勢！ 造成不便，我們深感抱歉。 「Jetpack」和「WooCommerce Shipping & Tax」外掛程式會免費安裝及啟用。','Zambézia'=>'贊比西亞','Tete'=>'太特','Sofala'=>'索法拉','Niassa'=>'尼亞薩','Nampula'=>'楠普拉','Maputo'=>'馬普托','Maputo Province'=>'馬普托省','Manica'=>'馬尼卡','Inhambane'=>'伊尼揚巴內','Gaza'=>'迦薩','Cabo Delgado'=>'德爾加杜角','Western North'=>'西北','Volta'=>'沃爾特','Upper West'=>'上西','Upper East'=>'上東','Savannah'=>'薩凡納','Oti'=>'奧蒂','North East'=>'東北','Greater Accra'=>'大阿克拉','Bono East'=>'東波諾','Bono'=>'波諾','Brong-Ahafo'=>'布朗阿哈福','Ashanti'=>'阿散蒂','Ahafo'=>'阿哈福','User&#8217;s WooCommerce payment tokens data.'=>'使用者的 WooCommerce 付款權杖資料。','User&#8217;s WooCommerce access to purchased downloads data.'=>'使用者的 WooCommerce 已購買下載項目資料存取權。','User&#8217;s WooCommerce purchased downloads data.'=>'使用者的 WooCommerce 已購買下載項目資料。','User&#8217;s WooCommerce orders data.'=>'使用者的 WooCommerce 訂單資料。','User&#8217;s WooCommerce customer data.'=>'使用者的 WooCommerce 顧客資料。','%s() was called before the Action Scheduler data store was initialized'=>'在 Action Scheduler 資料存放區初始化前，已呼叫 %s()','Your store\'s uploads directory is <a href="%1$s">browsable via the web</a>. We strongly recommend <a href="%2$s">configuring your web server to prevent directory indexing</a>.'=>'你可以<a href="%1$s">透過網頁瀏覽</a>商店的上傳目錄。我們強烈建議你<a href="%2$s">設定網頁伺服器以避免目錄建立索引</a>。','Finish setup'=>'完成設定','Take payments via bank transfer.'=>'透過銀行轉帳收款。','Take payments in cash upon delivery.'=>'貨到時收取現金款項。','Coupons discounts'=>'優惠券折扣','Shipment Tracking'=>'貨件追蹤','(opens in a new tab)'=>'(在新分頁中開啟)','WooCommerce.com support'=>'WooCommerce.com 支援','Installed version not tested with active version of WooCommerce %s'=>'安裝版本未與 WooCommerce 最新版本 %s 進行測試','%1$s (update to version %2$s is available)'=>'%1$s (可更新為版本 %2$s)','Please visit the <a href="%s" target="_blank">subscriptions page</a> and renew to continue receiving updates.'=>'請造訪<a href="%s" target="_blank">訂閱頁面</a>並續訂，方可繼續取得更新。','If checked, free shipping would be available based on pre-discount order amount.'=>'如果勾選這個選項，我們會根據折扣前的訂單金額提供免運服務。','Apply minimum order rule before coupon discount'=>'在使用優惠券折扣前套用最低訂單金額規則','For further assistance with WooCommerce core, use the <a href="%1$s">community forum</a>. For help with premium extensions sold on WooCommerce.com, <a href="%2$s">open a support request at WooCommerce.com</a>.'=>'如需 WooCommerce 核心使用者的進一步協助，請使用<a href="%1$s">社群論壇</a>。 如需進階版擴充功能 (WooCommerce.com 販售) 的相關協助，<a href="%2$s">請在 WooCommerce.com 開啟支援要求</a>。','Visit WooCommerce.com to learn more about <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">getting started</a>.'=>'造訪 WooCommerce.com，深入了解<a href="%1$s" target="_blank">使用者入門</a>。','Shipping Label'=>'運送標籤','Limit stats fields to the specified items.'=>'將統計資料欄位限定在指定項目。','The plugin could not be activated.'=>'無法啟用外掛程式。','Personalize homepage'=>'為首頁增添個人風格','Personalize your store\'s homepage'=>'為商店的首頁增添個人風格','The homepage is one of the most important entry points in your store. When done right it can lead to higher conversions and engagement. Don\'t forget to personalize the homepage that we created for your store during the onboarding.'=>'首頁是商店最重要的入口。如果設計得當，可以帶來更高的轉換率和互動次數。我們在新手入門教學時為你的商店建立了首頁，別忘了前往修改，展現自己的個人風格。','There was an error communicating with the WooPayments plugin.'=>'與 WooPayments 外掛程式連結時發生錯誤。','Securely accept credit and debit cards on your site. Manage transactions without leaving your WordPress dashboard. Only with <strong>WooPayments</strong>.'=>'在你的網站上安全地收受信用卡和簽帳金融卡。 不必離開 WordPress 儀表板就能管理交易。 一切收款便利功能，只在 <strong>WooPayments</strong>。','Try the new way to get paid'=>'嘗試付款新方法','It appears one or more database tables were missing. Attempting to re-create the missing table(s).'=>'似乎有一個以上的資料庫表格遺失。正在嘗試重新建立遺失的表格。','Your store is configured to serve digital products using "Redirect only" method. This method is deprecated, <a href="%s">please switch to a different method instead.</a><br><em>If you use a remote server for downloadable files (such as Google Drive, Dropbox, Amazon S3), you may optionally wish to "allow using redirects as a last resort". Enabling that and/or selecting any of the other options will make this notice go away.</em>'=>'你的商店已設定為使用「只重新導向」方法提供數位產品。 此方式已過時，<a href="%s">請改用其他方式。</a><br><em>如果你使用遠端伺服器下載可下載的檔案 (例如 Google Drive、Dropbox、Amazon S3)，可選擇「允許使用重新導向做為最後手段」。 啟用該選項和/或選取任何其他選項將使此通知消失。</em>','Get started'=>'開始使用','Send targeted campaigns, recover abandoned carts and much more with Mailchimp.'=>'使用 Mailchimp 針對廣告受眾傳送行銷活動傳單，以及購物車未結商品通知等等。','Set up payments'=>'設定付款','Securely accept credit and debit cards with one low rate, no surprise fees (custom rates available). Sell online and in store and track sales and inventory in one place.'=>'以單一低費率方式安全地接受信用卡和轉帳卡付款，不收取額外費用 (可自訂費率)。可在線上與實體店面中銷售，並在單一位置追蹤銷售狀況和存貨。','Choose the payment that you want, pay now, pay later or slice it. No credit card numbers, no passwords, no worries.'=>'選擇你希望的付款方式，然後選擇立即付款、稍後付款或分期付款。不需信用卡號，不需密碼，安全無虞。','Accept debit and credit cards in 135+ currencies, methods such as Alipay, and one-touch checkout with Apple Pay.'=>'接受超過 135 種貨幣的轉帳卡和信用卡、支付寶等付款方式，以及 Apple Pay 的單鍵快速結帳功能。','Store connected successfully.'=>'已成功連結商店。','Import your products'=>'匯入你的產品','Close dialog'=>'關閉對話方塊','Dismiss this notice'=>'關閉這項通知','🎉 Congrats on adding your first product!'=>'🎉 恭喜你新增了第一個產品！','Amount'=>'金額','CBD and other hemp-derived products'=>'CBD 和其他大麻衍生產品','Current page retrieval should be called on or after the `current_screen` hook.'=>'應在「current_screen」hook 或之後呼叫目前頁面擷取。','Action that should be completed to connect Jetpack.'=>'連結 Jetpack 應該完成的動作。','Plugin status.'=>'外掛程式狀態。','Plugin name.'=>'外掛程式名稱。','Plugin slug.'=>'外掛程式代稱。','There was