ue for the resulting set, or if any one of them is sufficient. Match affects the following parameters: status_is, status_is_not, product_includes, product_excludes, coupon_includes, coupon_excludes, customer, categories'=>'說明結果集的所有條件是否皆應為真，或者只要任一條件符合即足夠。比對會影響以下參數：status_is、status_is_not、product_includes、product_excludes、coupon_includes、coupon_excludes、customer、categories','Number of distinct products sold.'=>'售出的不同產品數量。','Average items per order'=>'每筆訂單的平均項目數量','Average order value.'=>'平均訂單金額。','Add additional piece of info about each category to the report.'=>'將各類別的其他資訊新增到報告中。','Limit result set to all items that have the specified term assigned in the categories taxonomy.'=>'將結果集限定在類別分類法中所有獲派指定字詞的項目。','User Name'=>'使用者名稱','Limit response to objects that don\'t have the specified user ids.'=>'將回應限定在沒有指定使用者 ID 的物件。','Limit response to objects that have the specified user ids.'=>'將回應限定在有指定使用者 ID 的物件。','Indicates whether all the conditions should be true for the resulting set, or if any one of them is sufficient. Match affects the following parameters: products, orders, username, ip_address.'=>'說明結果集的所有條件是否皆應為真，或者只要任一條件符合即足夠。比對會影響以下參數：products, orders, username, ip_address.','IP address for the downloader.'=>'下載程式的 IP 位址。','User name of the downloader.'=>'下載程式的使用者名稱。','User ID for the downloader.'=>'下載程式的使用者 ID。','The date of the download, as GMT.'=>'下載的日期 (以 GMT 格式顯示)。','The date of the download, in the site\'s timezone.'=>'下載的日期 (以網站時區顯示)。','Limit response to objects that don\'t have a specified ip address.'=>'將回應限定在沒有指定 IP 位址的物件。','Limit response to objects that have a specified ip address.'=>'將回應限定在有指定 IP 位址的物件。','Number of downloads.'=>'下載次數。','Limit result set to items assigned one or more tax rates.'=>'將結果集限定在獲派一個或多個稅率的項目。','Priority.'=>'優先順序。','State.'=>'州。','Sorry, fetching tax data failed.'=>'抱歉，擷取稅金資料失敗。','Limit result set to all items that have the specified term assigned in the taxes taxonomy.'=>'將結果集限定在稅金分類法中所有獲派指定字詞的項目。','Amount of tax codes.'=>'稅碼金額。',