Thanks for using {site_url}!'=>'感謝你使用 {site_url}！','Town / Village'=>'鎮/村','Postal code'=>'郵遞區號','Invalid field'=>'無效的欄位','Tax class slug already exists'=>'稅級代稱已存在','Tax class requires a valid name'=>'稅級須為有效的名稱','Additional content'=>'其他內容','Or you can download a pre-built version of the plugin from the <a href="%1$s">WordPress.org repository</a> or by visiting <a href="%2$s">the releases page in the GitHub repository</a>.'=>'或者你可以從 <a href="%1$s">WordPress.org 存放庫</a>下載預先建立的外掛程式版本，或者造訪 <a href="%2$s">GitHub 存放庫中的版本頁面</a>。','Text to appear below the main email content.'=>'顯示在主要電子郵件內容下方的文字。','Order not editable'=>'順序不可編輯','You do not have permission to install plugins.'=>'你沒有安裝外掛程式的權限。','Learn how to upgrade'=>'瞭解如何升級','The sale will start at 00:00:00 of "From" date and end at 23:59:59 of "To" date.'=>'銷售將在「開始」日期的 00:00:00 開始，並於「結束」日期的 23:59:59 結束。','Order fully refunded.'=>'訂單已全額退費。','Selecting no country / region to sell to prevents from completing the checkout. Continue anyway?'=>'不要選擇銷售國家/地區或區域，即可避免完成付款程序。 你要繼續操作嗎？','Please enter a valid Eircode.'=>'請輸入有效的 Eircode。','There was a failure fetching this action'=>'擷取此操作時發生故障','&larr; Back to "%s" attributes'=>'← 返回「%s」屬性','Note: WP CRON has been disabled on your install which may prevent this update from completing.'=>'請注意：已在你安裝的版本上停用 WP CRON，可能無法完成此更新。','Product display, sorting, and reports may not be accurate until this finishes. It will take a few minutes and this notice will disappear when complete.'=>'直到更新結束為止，產品顯示、排序和報告可能都不正確。這需要幾分鐘的時間，工作完成後就不會再顯示此通知。','You can manually run queued updates here.'=>'你可以在此處手動執行佇列更新。','Newest Scheduled Date'=>'最新排程日期','Oldest Scheduled Date'=>'最早排程日期','Count'=>'計數','Action Status'=>'動作狀態','Action Scheduler'=>'動作排程器','The %s class can only be run within WP CLI.'=>'%s 類別只能在 WP CLI 內執行。','Decrease existing stock by:'=>'藉由以下方減少現有庫存：','Increase existing stock by:'=>'藉由以下方增加現有庫存：','View progress &rarr;'=>'檢視進度 &rarr;','Learn more about updates'=>'深入瞭解更新內容','Update WooCommerce Database'=>'更新 WooCommerce 資料庫','The database update process runs in the background and may take a little while, so please be patient. Advanced users can alternatively update via %1$sWP CLI%2$s.'=>'資料庫更新程序會在背景執行，並可能須花費一段時間，請耐心等候。進階使用者可另外透過 %1$sWP CLI%2$s 進行更新。','WooCommerce has been updated! To keep things running smoothly, we have to update your database to the newest version.'=>'WooCommerce 已更新完成！為順暢執行工作，我們必須將您的資料庫更新至最新版本。','WooCommerce database update required'=>'必須進行 WooCommerce 資料庫更新','WooCommerce is updating the database in the background. The database update process may take a little while, so please be patient.'=>'WooCommerce 正在背景更新資料庫。資料庫更新程序可能須花費一段時間，請耐心等候。','[{site_title}]: Order #{order_number} has been cancelled'=>'[{site_title}]：Order #{order_number} 已取消','Updating database'=>'正在更新資料庫','Found %1$d updates (%2$s)'=>'已找到 %1$d 項更新 (%2$s)','No updates required. Database version is %s'=>'無須進行更新。資料庫版本為 %s','Stock: %d'=>'庫存：%d','Deleted %1$s and adjusted stock (%2$s)'=>'已刪除 %1$s 並調整庫存 (%2$s)','Invalid items'=>'無效項目','Invalid rate'=>'無效費率','Added line items: %s'=>'新增項目：%s','Your account was created successfully. Your login details have been sent to your email address.'=>'您的帳號已成功建立。您的登入詳細資料已傳送至您的電子郵件地址。','Your account was created successfully and a password has been sent to your email address.'=>'您的帳號已成功建立，且密碼已傳送至您的電子郵件地址。','WooCommerce is updating product data in the background'=>'WooCommerce 正在背景更新產品資料','Completed processing action %1$s with hook: %2$s'=>'使用 hook 完成處理動作 %1$s 與 hook: %2$s','Display suggestions within WooCommerce'=>'在 WooCommerce 內顯示建議','Show Suggestions'=>'顯示建議','We show contextual suggestions for official extensions that may be helpful to your store.'=>'我們會顯示與內容相關的建議，推薦對你的商店有幫助的官方擴充功能。','Marketplace suggestions'=>'Marketplace 建議','To opt out, leave this box unticked. Your store remains untracked, and no data will be collected. Read about what usage data is tracked at: %s.'=>'若要選擇退出，請勿勾選此核取方塊。由於你的商店保持取消追蹤狀態，我們不會收集任何資料。閱讀以了解我們會追蹤哪些使用資料：%s。','five star'=>