。你可以在<a target="_blank" href="%2$s">這裡</a>尋找正確的 Eircode。','Sorry, we do not have enough "%1$s" in stock to fulfill your order (%2$s available). We apologize for any inconvenience caused.'=>'很抱歉，我們的「%1$s」庫存不足，無法履行你的訂單 (可供應的數量為 %2$s)。造成不便，敬請見諒。','An identifier for the group this setting belongs to.'=>'此設定所屬的群組識別碼。','Variation status.'=>'變化版本狀態。','Invalid review ID.'=>'無效的評論 ID。','Limit result set to reviews assigned a specific status.'=>'將結果集限制為指派特定狀態的評論。','Limit result set to reviews assigned to specific product IDs.'=>'將結果集限制為指派給特定商品 ID 的評論。','Limit result set to that from a specific author email.'=>'將結果集限制為來自特定作者電子郵件。','The object cannot be deleted.'=>'物件無法刪除。','Unique identifier for the product that the review belongs to.'=>'評論所屬商品的唯一識別碼。','Product review field exceeds maximum length allowed.'=>'商品評論欄位超過最大字元數限制。','Cannot create existing product review.'=>'無法建立既有的商品評論。','Sorry, you are not allowed to change the comment type.'=>'抱歉，留言類型無法變更。','Updating review failed.'=>'更新評論失敗。','The object does not support trashing. Set \'%s\' to delete.'=>'物件不支援移至垃圾桶功能。設定「%s」以刪除。','Updating review status failed.'=>'更新評論狀態失敗。','If you copied over a template file to change something, then you will need to copy the new version of the template and apply your changes again.'=>'若你為了變更部分內容而複製了範本檔案，則你需要複製範本的新版本再重新套用變更。','Avatar URL with image size of %d pixels.'=>'圖片大小為 %d 像素的大頭貼 URL。','Limit result set to reviews assigned to specific user IDs.'=>'將結果集限制為指派給特定使用者 ID 的評論。','Unique identifier for the product.'=>'商品的唯一識別碼。','Supported features for this payment gateway.'=>'此付款閘道的支援功能。','Avatar URLs for the object reviewer.'=>'物件評論者的大頭貼 URL。','Limit response to reviews published before a given ISO8601 compliant date.'=>'將回應限制為指定 ISO8601 相容日期之前發佈的評論。','If true, this note will be attributed to the current user. If false, the note will be attributed to the system.'=>'其值為 true 時，此備註將歸於目前的使用者。其值為 false 時，此備註將歸於系統。','Order note author.'=>'訂單備註作者。','View affected templates'=>'檢視受影響的範本','Ensure result set excludes reviews assigned to specific user IDs.'=>'確保結果集排除指派給特定使用者 ID 的評論。','The object has already been trashed.'=>'物件已移至垃圾桶。','Update your theme to the latest version. If no update is available contact your theme author asking about compatibility with the current WooCommerce version.'=>'將佈景主題更新至最新版本。如果沒有可用的更新，請聯絡你的佈景主題作者，詢問與最新 WooCommerce 版本的相容性。','WooCommerce Customer Data'=>'WooCommerce 顧客資料','File ID.'=>'檔案 ID。','Controls the stock status of the product.'=>'控制產品的庫存狀態。','Status of the review.'=>'評論狀態。','Limit result set to products with specified stock status.'=>'限定結果為具特庫存狀態的商品。','Invalid review content.'=>'無效的評論內容。','Categories totals.'=>'分類總數。','Limit response to resources created after a given ISO8601 compliant date.'=>'將回應限制在指定 ISO8601 相容日期之後建立的資源。','Order Cancelled: #{order_number}'=>'已取消訂單：#{order_number}','Orders totals.'=>'訂單總計。','<strong>Your theme (%s) contains outdated copies of some WooCommerce template files.</strong> These files may need updating to ensure they are compatible with the current version of WooCommerce. Suggestions to fix this:'=>'<strong>你的佈景主題 (%s) 包含一些已過時的 WooCommerce 範本檔案副本。</strong>你可能需要更新這些檔案以確保與 WooCommerce 的最新版本相容。修正此問題的建議方式：','Placeholder image'=>'預留位置圖片','Enter attachment ID or URL to an image'=>'輸入附件 ID 或圖片 URL','Enter a number to set stock quantity at the variation level. Use a variation\'s \'Manage stock?\' check box above to enable/disable stock management at the variation level.'=>'輸入數字以設定變化版本層級的庫存數量。使用上方變化版本的「管理庫存？」核取方塊來啟用/停用變化版本層級的庫存管理功能。','This is the attachment ID, or image URL, used for placeholder images in the product catalog. Products with no image will use this.'=>'這是附件 ID (或圖片 URL)，用於商品目錄中的預留位置圖片。沒有圖片的商品將會使用此圖。','WooCommerce Services icon'=>'WooCommerce 服務圖示','If you\'d like to offer <span class="help_tip" data-tip="%1$s">live rates</span> from a specific carrier (e.g. UPS) you can find a variety of extensions available for WooCommerce <a href="%2$s" target="_blank">here</a>.'=>'若你想提供特定運輸業者 (例如 UPS) 的<span class="help_tip" data-tip="%1$s">即時費率</span>，可以在<a href="%2$s" target="_blank">這裡</a>尋找 WooCommerce 可用的各種擴充功能。','A live rate is the exact cost to ship an order, quoted directly from the shipping carrier.'=>'即時費率是直接由運輸業者報價的訂單實際運費。','ShipStation'=>'ShipStation','ShipStation icon'=>'ShipStation 圖示','We\'ll use %1$s for product weight and %2$s for product dimensions.'=>'我們的商品重量採用%1$s，商品尺寸採用%2$s。','Set up Stripe for me using this email:'=>'使用此電子郵件為我設定 Stripe：','WooCommerce PayPal Checkout Gateway'=>'WooCommerce PayPal 結帳閘道','Low stock amount'=>'低庫存量','Set up PayPal for me using this email:'=>'使用此電子郵件為我設定 PayPal：','We\'ve created two Shipping Zones - for %s and for the rest of the world. Below you can set Flat Rate shipping costs for these Zones or offer Free Shipping.'=>'我們建立了兩個運送區域，分別為%s和全球其餘區域。你可在下方為這些區域設定固定運費或提供免運費服務。','When handling an %s, should personal data within orders be retained or removed?'=>'處理%s時，是否會保留或是移除訂單中的個人資料？','When handling an %s, should access to downloadable files be revoked and download logs cleared?'=>'處理%s時，是否會撤銷可下載檔案的存取權限並清除下載記錄？','Which product category should be exported?'=>'應匯出哪個商品分類？','Export all categories'=>'匯出所有分類','We recommend using ShipStation to save time at the post office by printing your shipping labels at home. Try ShipStation free for 30 days.'=>'建議你在家使用 ShipStation 列印郵寄標籤，省下在郵局處理包裹的時間。免費試用 ShipStation 30 天。','Alto Paraguay'=>'Alto Paraguay','Presidente Hayes'=>'Presidente Hayes','Amambay'=>'Amambay','Central'=>'Central','Cordillera'=>'Cordillera','San Pedro'=>'San Pedro','Centimeters'=>'公分','Item moved up'=>'商品已向上移動','Item moved down'=>'商品已向下移動','Kilograms'=>'公斤','Pounds'=>'磅','Grams'=>'克','Meters'=>'公尺','Millimeters'=>'公釐','Inches'=>'英寸','Yards'=>'英碼','Ounces'=>'盎司','Sud Sardegna'=>'Sud Sardegna','Are you sure you want to remove the selected items?'=>'你確定要移除選取的商品？','You may need to manually restore the item\'s stock.'=>'你可能需要手動還原該商品的庫存。','%d API key permanently revoked.'=>'%d API 金鑰已永久撤銷。','Apartment, suite, unit, etc.'=>'公寓、套房、單位等','Cannot set attributes due to invalid parent product.'=>'由於上層產品無效，因此無法設定屬性。','This action cannot be reversed. Are you sure you wish to erase personal data from the selected orders?'=>'此動作無法復原。確定要將個人資料從選取的訂單中刪除？','Shipping Address'=>'運送地址','Billing Address'=>'帳單地址','Shipping Address 1'=>'運送地址 1','Billing Address 1'=>'帳單地址 1','Payer PayPal address'=>'付款人 PayPal 地址','Payer last name'=>'付款人姓氏','Payer first name'=>'付款人名字','MySQL version string.'=>'MySQL 版本字串。','Your CSV needs to include columns in a specific order. %1$sClick here to download a sample%2$s.'=>'你的 CSV 必須包含特定順序的欄位。%1$s按一下此處以下載範例%2$s。','This will be how your name will be displayed in the account section and in reviews'=>'你的名稱在帳號區段和評論中看起來就像這樣','terms and conditions'=>'條款與條件','privacy policy'=>'隱私權政策','United States (US) dollar'=>'美元','PayPal allows us to send one address. If you are using PayPal for shipping labels you may prefer to send the shipping address rather than billing. Turning this option off may prevent PayPal Seller protection from applying.'=>'PayPal 只允許一個運送地址。如果你使用 PayPal 的郵寄標籤，那麼你可能會想要配送到運送地址，而不是帳單地址。關閉此選項可能會導致無法實施 PayPal 賣家保護措施。','eCheck ending in %1$s'=>'結尾為 %1$s 的電子支票','PayPal Standard redirects customers to PayPal to enter their payment information.'=>'PayPal 網站付款標準版會將顧客重新導向至 PayPal，讓他們在那裡輸入自己的付款資訊。','Other locations'=>'其他地點','%1$s &ndash; %2$s'=>'%1$s – %2$s','%1$s (#%2$s)'=>'%1$s (#%2$s)','Any &quot;%1$s&quot; method'=>'任何「%1$s」方式','Account details:'=>'帳號詳細資料：','Comma-separated list of search stopwords in your languageabout,an,are,as,at,be,by,com,for,from,how,in,is,it,of,on,or,that,the,this,to,was,what,when,where,who,will,with,www'=>'about,an,are,as,at,be,by,com,for,from,how,in,is,it,of,on,or,that,the,this,to,was,what,when,where,who,will,with,www','Optionally add some text for the terms checkbox that customers must accept.'=>'另可選擇為顧客須接受的條款核取方塊新增一段文字。','%s page'=>'%s 頁面','No page set'=>'未設定任何頁面','Highlight required fields with an asterisk'=>'用星號標出必填欄位','Required'=>'必填','These options let you change the appearance of the WooCommerce checkout.'=>'你可以使用這些選項來改變 WooCommerce 結帳頁面的外觀。','Please see the <a href="https://www.paypal.com/us/webapps/mpp/ua/privacy-full">PayPal Privacy Policy</a> for more details.'=>'請參閱 <a href="https://www.paypal.com/us/webapps/mpp/ua/privacy-full">PayPal 隱私權政策</a>以取得更多詳細資料。','We accept payments through PayPal. When processing payments, some of your data will be passed to PayPal, including information required to process or support the payment, such as the purchase total and billing information.'=>'我們接受透過 PayPal 付款。處理付款時，會將你的部分資料傳送給 PayPal，包括處理或支援付款所需的資訊 (例如購買總金額和帳單資訊)。','Take payments in person via checks. This offline gateway can also be useful to test purchases.'=>'透過支票親自收款。這個離線閘道亦可用於測試購買項目，相當實用。','Take payments in person via BACS. More commonly known as direct bank/wire transfer.'=>'透過 BACS 親自收款。 更常見的說法是銀行/轉帳/電匯。','I have read and agree to the website %s'=>'我已閱讀並同意網站的〈%s〉','%s field'=>'[%s] 欄位','In this subsection you should list which third party payment processors you’re using to take payments on your store since these may handle customer data. We’ve included PayPal as an example, but you should remove this if you’re not using PayPal.'=>'你應該在此次區段中列出你的商店用來接受付款的第三方付款處理單位，因為這些單位可能會涉及客戶資料處理。我們已將 PayPal 加入做為範例，但如果你並未使用 PayPal，請移除此項目。','We share information with third parties who help us provide our orders and store services to you; for example --'=>'我們會與協助我們提供你訂單和商店服務的第三方共用資訊；例如：','In this section you should list who you’re sharing data with, and for what purpose. This could include, but may not be limited to, analytics, marketing, payment gateways, shipping providers, and third party embeds.'=>'你應在此區段中列出你共用資訊的對象與目的。這可能包括但不限於分析、行銷、付款閘道、貨運供應商及第三方嵌入項目。','What we share with others'=>'我們與他人共用的項目','Our team members have access to this information to help fulfill orders, process refunds and support you.'=>'我們的團隊成員可存取此資訊以協助履行訂單、處理退款和為你提供支援。','Customer information like your name, email address, and billing and shipping information.'=>'你的姓名、電子郵件地址以及帳單和運送資料等客戶資訊。','Order information like what was purchased, when it was purchased and where it should be sent, and'=>'購買項目、時間和傳送目的地等訂購資訊，以及','Members of our team have access to the information you provide us. For example, both Administrators and Shop Managers can access:'=>'我們的團隊成員可存取你提供給我們的資料。例如，管理員和商店經理均可存取以下資料：','Who on our team has access'=>'擁有存取權的團隊成員','We will also store comments or reviews, if you choose to leave them.'=>'如果你選擇留下留言和評論，我們也會儲存這些內容。','We generally store information about you for as long as we need the information for the purposes for which we collect and use it, and we are not legally required to continue to keep it. For example, we will store order information for XXX years for tax and accounting purposes. This includes your name, email address and billing and shipping addresses.'=>'我們通常只會在出於收集和使用的目的而需要這些資訊時，才會儲存有關你的資訊，在法律上我們並不需要繼續保留這些資訊。例如，我們會為了稅務和會計目的而儲存訂單資訊 XXX 年。這包括你的姓名、電子郵件地址以及帳單和運送地址。','If you create an account, we will store your name, address, email and phone number, which will be used to populate the checkout for future orders.'=>'如果你建立帳號，我們將會儲存你的姓名、地址、電子郵件和電話號碼，以便在日後用於訂單自動填入結帳資訊。','Send you marketing messages, if you choose to receive them'=>'傳送行銷訊息給你 (如果你已同意接收)','Improve our store offerings'=>'改善商店優惠內容','Comply with any legal obligations we have, such as calculating taxes'=>'遵循法律義務，例如計算稅額','Set up your account for our store'=>'開設你在我們商店的帳號','Process payments and prevent fraud'=>'處理付款和防範詐騙','Respond to your requests, including refunds and complaints'=>'回覆你的申請，包括退款要求或客訴。','Send you information about your account and order'=>'將帳號和訂單相關資訊傳送給你','When you purchase from us, we’ll ask you to provide information including your name, billing address, shipping address, email address, phone number, credit card/payment details and optional account information like username and password. We’ll use this information for purposes, such as, to:'=>'當你向我們購買產品時，我們會要求你提供一些資訊，包括你的姓名、帳單地址、運送地址、電子郵件地址、電話號碼、信用卡/付款詳細資料以及選填的帳號資訊 (例如使用者名稱和密碼)。我們會將這個資訊用於以下的用途，例如：','Note: you may want to further detail your cookie policy, and link to that section from here.'=>'附註：你可能想要進一步瞭解 Cookie 政策，請從這裡連結至該區段。','We’ll also use cookies to keep track of cart contents while you’re browsing our site.'=>'我們也會使用 Cookie 來追蹤你在瀏覽我們網站時的購物車內容。','Shipping address: we’ll ask you to enter this so we can, for instance, estimate shipping before you place an order, and send you the order!'=>'運送地址：舉例來說，我們會要求你輸入運送地址，以便在你下訂單前估算運費，然後將訂單傳送給你！','Location, IP address and browser type: we’ll use this for purposes like estimating taxes and shipping'=>'位置、IP 位址和瀏覽器類型：我們會利用此資訊來估算稅額和運費','Products you’ve viewed: we’ll use this to, for example, show you products you’ve recently viewed'=>'你已檢視過的商品：例如，我們會運用此資訊來顯示你最近瀏覽過的商品。','While you visit our site, we’ll track:'=>'在你造訪我們的網站時，我們會追蹤以下項目：','What we collect and store'=>'我們收集和儲存的內容','We collect information about you during the checkout process on our store.'=>'你在我們商店中進行結帳的過程中，我們會收集你的相關資訊。','This sample language includes the basics around what personal data your store may be collecting, storing and sharing, as well as who may have access to that data. Depending on what settings are enabled and which additional plugins are used, the specific information shared by your store will vary. We recommend consulting with a lawyer when deciding what information to disclose on your privacy policy.'=>'此範例語言包括你的商店可能正在收集、儲存和共用哪些個人資料以及誰可以存取該資料等基本資訊。視啟用的設定以及使用的外掛程式而定，你的商店所分享的具體資訊內容可能會有所不同。我們建議你決定在隱私權政策中揭露哪些資訊前，請先諮詢律師。','Browser User Agent'=>'瀏覽器使用者代理程式','Items Purchased'=>'已購買的項目','Order Number'=>'訂單號碼','Access granted'=>'已授予存取權','Download count'=>'下載計數','Token'=>'代碼','Payment Tokens'=>'付款代碼','User email'=>'使用者電子郵件地址','Personal data removed.'=>'個人資料已移除。','Shipping State'=>'運送州','Shipping Postal/Zip Code'=>'運送地郵遞區號','Shipping City'=>'運送城市','Shipping Company'=>'收件公司','Shipping Last Name'=>'收件人姓氏','Shipping First Name'=>'收件人名字','Phone Number'=>'電話號碼','Billing State'=>'帳單寄送州','Billing Postal/Zip Code'=>'帳單寄送地郵遞區號','Billing City'=>'帳單寄送城市','Billing Company'=>'帳單收件公司','Billing Last Name'=>'帳單收件人姓氏','Billing First Name'=>'帳單收件人名字','Download ID'=>'下載 ID','Customer Data'=>'顧客資料','Error during status transition.'=>'狀態轉換期間發生錯誤。','Update status event failed.'=>'更新狀態事件失敗。','Payment complete event failed.'=>'付款完成事件失敗。','optional'=>'選填','Display name'=>'顯示名稱','Display name cannot be changed to email address due to privacy concern.'=>'為保護隱私，顯示名稱不得變更為電子郵件地址。','Please read and accept the terms and conditions to proceed with your order.'=>'請詳閱並接受條款與條件，以繼續處理你的訂單。','Cloning is forbidden.'=>'禁止複製。','Deleted all active sessions, and %d saved carts.'=>'已刪除所有作用中的工作階段及 %d 個已儲存的購物車。','This tool will delete all customer session data from the database, including current carts and saved carts in the database.'=>'這個工具會清除資料庫中所有顧客工作階段資料，包括目前使用的購物車和資料庫中儲存的購物車。','If the payment was refunded via the API.'=>'如果是透過 API 退款。','Order total formatted for locale'=>'根據地區設定調整訂單總額的格式','%1$s has been removed from your cart because it has since been modified. You can add it back to your cart <a href="%2$s">here</a>.'=>'%1$s 已修改，因此已從你的購物車中移除。你可以在<a href="%2$s">這裡</a>將它重新放入購物車。','Name of the customer for the order'=>'訂單的顧客姓名','URL to edit the order'=>'可前往編輯訂單的 URL','Blog id of the record on the multisite.'=>'多站點上記錄的網誌 ID。','Your store does not appear to be using a secure connection. We highly recommend serving your entire website over an HTTPS connection to help keep customer data secure. <a href="%s">Learn more here.</a>'=>'你的商店似乎沒有使用安全的連線。強烈建議你為整個網站使用 HTTPS 連線，這麼做有助於保護顧客資料安全無虞。<a href="%s">需深入瞭解請按這裡。</a>','Access to Purchased Downloads'=>'存取已購買的下載項目','Purchased Downloads'=>'已購買的下載項目','Removed payment token "%d"'=>'已移除的付款代碼「%d」','Customer download permissions have been retained.'=>'已保留客戶下載權限。','Removed access to downloadable files.'=>'已移除可下載檔案的存取權限。','Personal data within order %s has been retained.'=>'已保留 %s 訂單中的個人資料。','Removed personal data from order %s.'=>'已移除 %s 訂單的個人資料。','Removed customer "%s"'=>'已移除客戶「%s」','User roleShop manager'=>'商店經理','User roleCustomer'=>'客戶','Unable to create order.'=>'無法建立訂單。','%d permissions deleted'=>'已刪除的 %d 權限','This tool will delete expired download permissions and permissions with 0 remaining downloads.'=>'此工具將刪除已過期的下載權限以及 0 個剩餘下載項目的權限。','Clean up download permissions'=>'清除下載權限','Used-up download permissions'=>'用盡下載權限','Limit result set to products with a specific attribute. Use the taxonomy name/attribute slug.'=>'透過特定屬性設定產品的限制結果。使用分類名稱/屬性代稱。','Unserializing instances of this class is forbidden.'=>'禁止取消這個類別執行個體的序列化。','display name%1$s %2$s'=>'%2$s %1$s','WooCommerce pages'=>'WooCommerce 頁面','WooCommerce database version'=>'WooCommerce 資料庫版本','Displays whether or not WordPress is using an external object cache.'=>'顯示 WordPress 是否正在使用外部物件快取。','External object cache'=>'外部物件快取','WordPress cron'=>'WordPress Cron','WordPress debug mode'=>'WordPress 偵錯模式','WordPress memory limit'=>'WordPress 記憶體限制','WordPress multisite'=>'WordPress 多站點','%1$s - There is a newer version of WordPress available (%2$s)'=>'%1$s - 有新版的 WordPress 可用 (%2$s)','WordPress version'=>'WordPress 版本','WooCommerce version'=>'WooCommerce 版本','Settings tab labelPayments'=>'付款','Enable coupons'=>'啟用優惠券','Rates will be configurable and taxes will be calculated during checkout.'=>'可設定稅率，且結帳時會計算稅額。','Enable tax rates and calculations'=>'啟用稅率及稅額計算','Manage'=>'管理','Account endpoints'=>'帳號端點','Secure checkout'=>'安全結帳','Legacy API'=>'舊版 API','Retain completed orders for a specified duration before anonymizing the personal data within them.'=>'將已完成的訂單保留一定期間，過後再匿名處理訂單中的個人資料。','Retain completed orders'=>'保留已完成的訂單','Retain cancelled orders'=>'保留已取消的訂單','Failed orders are unpaid and may have been abandoned by the customer. They will be trashed after the specified duration.'=>'失敗的訂單並未付款，可能是客戶放棄該筆訂單。在一定期間過後，這些資料就會移至垃圾桶。','Retain failed orders'=>'保留失敗的訂單','Pending orders are unpaid and may have been abandoned by the customer. They will be trashed after the specified duration.'=>'待確認的訂單並未付款，可能是客戶放棄該筆訂單。在一定期間過後，這些資料就會移至垃圾桶。','Cancelled orders are unpaid and may have been cancelled by the store owner or customer. They will be trashed after the specified duration.'=>'取消的訂單並未付款，可能是由商店擁有者或客戶取消。 在一定期間過後，這些訂單就會移至垃圾桶。','Optionally add some text about your store privacy policy to show during checkout.'=>'另可選擇新增一段有關商店隱私權政策的文字，在結帳時顯示。','Checkout privacy policy'=>'結帳隱私權政策','Optionally add some text about your store privacy policy to show on account registration forms.'=>'另可選擇新增一段有關商店隱私權政策的文字，在帳號註冊表單上顯示。','Registration privacy policy'=>'註冊隱私權政策','privacy page'=>'隱私權頁面','Privacy policy'=>'隱私權政策','Filter by registered customer'=>'依已註冊的顧客篩選','Remove personal data'=>'移除個人資料','Use previous column mapping preferences?'=>'使用先前的欄對應喜好設定？','Retain pending orders '=>'保留待確認的訂單','Inactive accounts are those which have not logged in, or placed an order, for the specified duration. They will be deleted. Any orders will be converted into guest orders.'=>'閒置的帳號是指有一定期間未登入或下訂單的帳號。這些帳號將會遭到刪除。任何訂單都將會轉換為訪客訂單。','Retain inactive accounts '=>'保留閒置的帳號','Choose how long to retain personal data when it\'s no longer needed for processing. Leave the following options blank to retain this data indefinitely.'=>'選擇不再需要使用個人資料來處理訂單時，要將個人資料保留多久。將以下選項留空，以便無限期保留該資料。','Personal data retention'=>'個人資料保留','Account erasure requests'=>'帳號清除要求','Allowed emails'=>'允許的電子郵件','Your personal data will be used to process your order, support your experience throughout this website, and for other purposes described in our %s.'=>'我們會使用你的個人資料來處理你的訂單、支援你在本網站中的使用體驗，以及用於%s中說明的其他用途。','Your personal data will be used to support your experience throughout this website, to manage access to your account, and for other purposes described in our %s.'=>'我們會使用你的個人資料來支援你在本網站中的使用體驗、管理你的帳號存取權，以及用於%s中說明的其他用途。','This section controls the display of your website privacy policy. The privacy notices below will not show up unless a %s is set.'=>'這個區段用於控制網站隱私權政策的顯示方式。 必須設定%s，才會顯示下方的隱私權聲明。','Accounts &amp; Privacy'=>'帳號及隱私權','List of allowed billing emails to check against when an order is placed. Separate email addresses with commas. You can also use an asterisk (*) to match parts of an email. For example "*@gmail.com" would match all gmail addresses.'=>'下訂單時用於比對的允許帳單電子郵件清單。 請用逗號分隔電子郵件地址。 你可以使用星號 (*) 來比對電子郵件地址的其中一部分。 例如使用「*@gmail.com」比對所有 gmail 地址。','Removed personal data from %s order.'=>'已移除 %s 筆訂單中的個人資料。','View &amp; Customize'=>'檢視和自訂','Review Settings'=>'檢閱設定','Visit Dashboard'=>'造訪儀表板','You can also:'=>'你也可以：','You\'re ready to add products to your store.'=>'你已經準備好為你的商店新增產品。','Create some products'=>'建立一些產品','Continue with WooCommerce Services'=>'繼續使用 WooCommerce 服務','Connect your store to activate WooCommerce Services'=>'連結至你的商店並啟用 WooCommerce 服務','Thanks for using Jetpack! Your store is almost ready: to activate services like %s, just connect your store.'=>'感謝你使用 Jetpack！你的商店即將準備就緒：若要啟用 %s 之類的服務，只要連結你的商店即可。','automated taxes icon'=>'自動計算稅額圖示','Save time and errors with automated tax calculation and collection at checkout. Powered by WooCommerce Services and Jetpack.'=>'在結帳時使用自動計算稅額及收集功能，可節省時間和減少錯誤。由 WooCommerce 服務和 Jetpack 提供。','Storefront icon'=>'Storefront 圖示','Mailchimp for WooCommerce'=>'Mailchimp for WooCommerce','Mailchimp icon'=>'Mailchimp 圖示','Join the 16 million customers who use Mailchimp. Sync list and store data to send automated emails, and targeted campaigns.'=>'加入 1600 萬名使用 Mailchimp 的顧客行列。同步清單和商店資料，以便發送自動電子郵件和目標式行銷活動。','Mailchimp'=>'Mailchimp','Design your store with deep WooCommerce integration. If toggled on, we’ll install <a href="https://woocommerce.com/storefront/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Storefront</a>, and your current theme <em>%s</em> will be deactivated.'=>'藉由深入的 WooCommerce 整合設計你的商店。 如果開啟，我們將會安裝 <a href="https://woocommerce.com/storefront/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Storefront</a>，並停用你目前使用的 <em>%s</em> 佈景主題。','Enhance your store with these recommended free features.'=>'運用這些推薦的免費功能改善你的網站。','Recommended for All WooCommerce Stores'=>'推薦所有 WooCommerce 商店使用','The PayFast extension for WooCommerce enables you to accept payments by Credit Card and EFT via one of South Africa’s most popular payment gateways. No setup fees or monthly subscription costs.'=>'使用 WooCommerce 的 PayFast 延伸模組，便能透過南非最受歡迎的其中一個付款閘道，使用信用卡和 EFT 收款。無需支付設定費或訂閱月費。','The eWAY extension for WooCommerce allows you to take credit card payments directly on your store without redirecting your customers to a third party site to make payment.'=>'使用 WooCommerce 的 eWAY 延伸模組，便能直接在商店中收取信用卡付款，不需要將顧客重新導向至第三方網站進行付款。','WooCommerce PayFast Gateway'=>'WooCommerce PayFast 閘道','WooCommerce eWAY Gateway'=>'WooCommerce eWAY 閘道','WooCommerce Square'=>'WooCommerce Square','Klarna Payments for WooCommerce'=>'Klarna Payments for WooCommerce','Klarna Checkout for WooCommerce'=>'Klarna Checkout for WooCommerce','WooCommerce Stripe Gateway'=>'WooCommerce Stripe 閘道','The following plugins will be installed and activated for you:'=>'系統會為你安裝和啟用下列外掛程式：','What currency do you accept payments in?'=>'你接受使用哪種貨幣付款？','Choose a state&hellip;'=>'選擇州…','Recommended'=>'推薦','Year(s)'=>'年','Month(s)'=>'月','Week(s)'=>'週','Day(s)'=>'天','You don&#8217;t have permission to do this.'=>'你沒有執行此操作的權限。','Insufficient privileges to import products.'=>'權限不足，無法匯入產品。','Insufficient privileges to export products.'=>'權限不足，無法匯出產品。','Loading network orders'=>'正在載入網路訂單','You do not have permission to edit API Keys'=>'你沒有編輯 API 金鑰的權限。','REST API'=>'REST API','No keys found.'=>'找不到金鑰。','Return to payments'=>'返回付款','Yasothon'=>'益梭通府','Yala'=>'也拉府','Uttaradit'=>'程逸府','Uthai Thani'=>'烏泰他尼府','Udon Thani'=>'烏隆府','Ubon Ratchathani'=>'烏汶府','Trat'=>'達叻府','Trang'=>'董里府','Tak'=>'達府','Surin'=>'素林府','Surat Thani'=>'素叻府','Suphan Buri'=>'素攀武里府','Sukhothai'=>'素可泰府','Songkhla'=>'宋卡府','Sisaket'=>'四色菊府','Sing Buri'=>'信武里府','Satun'=>'沙敦府','Saraburi'=>'北標府','Samut Songkhram'=>'夜功府','Samut Sakhon'=>'龍仔厝府','Samut Prakan'=>'北欖府','Sakon Nakhon'=>'色軍府','Sa Kaeo'=>'沙繳府','Roi Et'=>'黎逸府','Rayong'=>'羅勇府','Ratchaburi'=>'叻丕府','Ranong'=>'腊農府','Prac