s may not be shown until you <a href="%s" target="_blank">Regenerate Thumbnails</a>.'=>'發佈變更之後，在你<a href="%s" target="_blank">重新產生縮圖</a>之前，可能不會顯示新的圖片大小。','After publishing your changes, new image sizes will be generated automatically.'=>'發佈變更之後，新的圖片大小將會自動產生。','Thumbnail regeneration has been scheduled to run in the background.'=>'縮圖重新產生作業已排程於背景中執行。','This will regenerate all shop thumbnails to match your theme and/or image settings.'=>'這將會重新產生全部的商店縮圖，以配合你的佈景主題及/或圖片設定。','Regenerate'=>'重新產生','Regenerate shop thumbnails'=>'重新產生商店縮圖','Thumbnail regeneration is running in the background. Depending on the amount of images in your store this may take a while.'=>'縮圖重新產生作業正在背景中執行。視商店中的圖片數量而定，這可能需要一段時間才能完成。','Cancel thumbnail regeneration'=>'取消縮圖重新產生作業','Change order status to completed'=>'將訂單狀態變更為「已完成」','Change order status to processing'=>'將訂單狀態變更為「處理中」','Change order status to on-hold'=>'將訂單狀態變更為「暫停」','Edit this order'=>'編輯此訂單','This is the default category and it cannot be deleted. It will be automatically assigned to products with no category.'=>'此為預設分類，無法刪除。系統會自動將其指派給沒有分類的產品。','Make &#8220;%s&#8221; the default category'=>'將「%s」設為預設分類','Deleting a category does not delete the products in that category. Instead, products that were only assigned to the deleted category are set to the category %s.'=>'刪除某個分類並不會刪除該分類中的產品。僅歸類在已刪除分類下的產品，則會設定至「%s」分類下。','Cancelled product image regeneration job.'=>'已取消產品圖片重新產生作業。','%s quantity'=>'%s 數量','Pay for this order'=>'支付這筆訂單','Sandbox API signature'=>'Sandbox API signature','Sandbox API password'=>'Sandbox API password','Sandbox API username'=>'Sandbox API username','Live API signature'=>'Live API signature','Live API password'=>'Live API password','Live API username'=>'Live API username','Invalid webhook.'=>'無效的 webhook。','1:1'=>'1:1','Thumbnail cropping'=>'縮圖裁剪','Product Images'=>'商品圖片','Rows per page'=>'每頁行數','Enable store notice'=>'啟用商店通知','Store Notice'=>'商店通知','The maximum allowed setting is %d'=>'允許的最大設定值為 %d','The minimum allowed