ustomer download log'=>'客戶下載的紀錄','Copy link'=>'複製連結','Status:'=>'狀態:','Date created:'=>'建立日期:','Municipality / District'=>'自治區 / 行政區','%s is not a valid postcode / ZIP.'=>'%s 不是有效的郵遞區號。','Error processing refund. Please try again.'=>'處理退款時發生錯誤。請再試一次。','Limit result set to products with specific SKU(s). Use commas to separate.'=>'將結果集限制為具有特定 SKU 的產品。以逗號分隔。','Shop pages'=>'商店頁面','No customer downloads found.'=>'找不到客戶下載項目。','Permission #%d not found.'=>'找不到權限 #%d。','Confirm navigation'=>'確認導覽','This report link has expired. %1$sClick here to view the filtered report%2$s.'=>'此報告連結已到期。%1$s按一下這裡檢視篩選報告%2$s。','Set Status - On backorder'=>'設定狀態 - 延期交貨','Copying to clipboard failed. You should be able to right-click the button and copy.'=>'無法複製到剪貼簿。你應該能用滑鼠右鍵按一下按鈕，然後複製。','Paid on %1$s @ %2$s'=>'在 %2$s @ %1$s 付費','Filter by stock status'=>'依存貨狀態篩選','On backorder'=>'延期交貨','Postcodes containing wildcards (e.g. CB23*) or fully numeric ranges (e.g. <code>90210...99000</code>) are also supported. Please see the shipping zones <a href="%s" target="_blank">documentation</a> for more information.'=>'系統也支援包含萬用字元 (例如 CB23*) 或完整數字範圍 (例如 <code>90210...99000</code>) 的郵遞區號。 如需詳細資訊，請參閱送貨區域<a href="%s" target="_blank">文件</a>。','Change status: '=>'變更狀態：','Completed'=>'已完成','On-hold'=>'暫停','Payment via'=>'透過以下方式付款','Change status to completed'=>'將狀態變更為已完成','Change status to processing'=>'將狀態變更為處理中','Create your first coupon'=>'建立第一張優惠券','Existing products that match by ID or SKU will be updated. Products that do not exist will be skipped.'=>'符合 ID 或 SKU 的現有產品將會更新。系統會略過不存在的產品。','Change status to on-hold'=>'將狀態變更為保留中','To receive updates and support for this extension, you need to <strong>purchase</strong> a new subscription or consolidate your extensions to one connected account by <strong><a href="%1$s" title="Sharing Docs">sharing</a> or <a href="%2$s" title="Transferring Docs">transferring</a></strong> this extension to this connected account.'=>'若要收到此延伸模組的更新和支援，你必須<strong>購買</strong>新的訂閱，或者將你的延伸模組整併到已連結的帳號 (方法如下：將此延伸模組<strong><a href="%1$s" title="分享文件">分享</a>或<a href="%2$s" title="轉移文件">轉移</a></strong>至該帳號)。','M j, Y'=>'Y 年 n 月 j 日','%s = human-readable time difference%s ago'=>'%s前','The WooCommerce Helper plugin is no longer needed. <a href="%s">Manage subscriptions</a> from the extensions tab instead.'=>'你已不再需要 WooCommerce Helper 外掛程式。可以改用擴充功能分頁<a href="%s">管理訂閱</a>。','Reasons you\'ll love Jetpack'=>'你會愛上 Jetpack 的原因','payment setup'=>'付款設定','payment setup and automated taxes'=>'付款設定和自動計算稅額','Webhook topic unknown. Please select a valid topic.'=>'Webhook 主題不明。請選擇有效的主題。','Delete "%s" permanently'=>'永久刪除「%s」','Continue with Jetpack'=>'繼續使用 Jetpack','Square'=>'Square','Klarna Payments'=>'Klarna 付款','Klarna Checkout'=>'Klarna 結帳','Email address to receive payments'=>'收取款項的電子郵件地址','Direct payments to email address:'=>'直接付款至電子郵件地址：','Securely accept credit and debit cards with one low rate, no surprise fees (custom rates available). Sell online and in store and track sales and inventory in one place. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Learn more about Square</a>.'=>'以安全的單一低費率方式接受信用卡和轉帳卡付款，不收取額外費用 (可自訂費率)。可在線上與實體店面中銷售，並在單一位置追蹤銷售狀況和存貨。<a href="%s" target="_blank">深入瞭解 Square</a>。','Choose the payment that you want, pay now, pay later or slice it. No credit card numbers, no passwords, no worries. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Learn more about Klarna</a>.'=>'選擇你希望的付款方式，然後選擇立即付款、稍後付款或分期付款。不需信用卡號，不需密碼，安全無虞。<a href="%s" target="_blank">深入瞭解 Klarna</a>。','Full checkout experience with pay now, pay later and slice it. No credit card numbers, no passwords, no worries. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Learn more about Klarna</a>.'=>'提供立即付款、稍後付款或分期付款的完整結帳體驗。不需信用卡號，不需密碼，安全無虞。<a href="%s" target="_blank">深入瞭解 Klarna</a>。','Accept debit and credit cards in 135+ currencies, methods such as Alipay, and one-touch checkout with Apple Pay. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Learn more</a>.'=>'接受超過 135 種貨幣的轉帳卡和信用卡、支付寶等付款方式，以及 Apple Pay 的單鍵快速結帳功能。<a href="%s" target="_blank">瞭解更多</a>。','I will also be selling products or services in person.'=>'我也會親自銷售產品或服務。','Customer downloads'=>'客戶下載項目','Revision restored.'=>'已還原修訂版本。','If you like, you may enter custom structures for your product URLs here. For example, using <code>shop</code> would make your product links like <code>%sshop/sample-product/</code>. This setting affects product URLs only, not things such as product categories.'=>'若有需要，你可以在這裡輸入產品網址的自訂結構。例如，使用 <code>shop</code> 會讓你的產品連結看起來像 <code>%sshop/sample-product/</code>。這項設定只會影響產品網址，不會影響產品類別等項目。','Simiyu'=>'Simiyu','Njombe'=>'Njombe','Katavi'=>'Katavi','Geita'=>'Geita','Manyara'=>'Manyara','Tanga'=>'Tanga','Tabora'=>'Tabora','Singida'=>'Singida','Shinyanga'=>'Shinyanga','Ruvuma'=>'Ruvuma','Rukwa'=>'Rukwa','Coast'=>'Coast','Mwanza'=>'Mwanza','Mtwara'=>'Mtwara','Morogoro'=>'Morogoro','Zanzibar West'=>'Zanzibar West','Mbeya'=>'Mbeya','Mara'=>'Mara','Lindi'=>'Lindi','Zanzibar South'=>'Zanzibar South','Pemba South'=>'Pemba South','Kilimanjaro'=>'Kilimanjaro','Kigoma'=>'Kigoma','Zanzibar North'=>'Zanzibar North','Pemba North'=>'Pemba North','Kagera'=>'Kagera','Iringa'=>'Iringa','Dodoma'=>'Dodoma','Dar es Salaam'=>'Dar es Salaam','Arusha'=>'Arusha','Ungheni'=>'Ungheni','Taraclia'=>'Taraclia','Soroca'=>'Soroca','Rezina'=>'Rezina','Orhei'=>'Orhei','Nisporeni'=>'Nisporeni','Leova'=>'Leova','Ialoveni'=>'Ialoveni','Glodeni'=>'Glodeni','Drochia'=>'Drochia','Criuleni'=>'Criuleni','Move &#8220;%s&#8221; to the Trash'=>'將「%s」移至垃圾桶','Attributes let you define extra product data, such as size or color. You can use these attributes in the shop sidebar using the "layered nav" widgets.'=>'屬性可讓你定義額外的產品資料，例如大小或顏色。你可以透過「多層式導覽」小工具在商店側邊列使用這些屬性。','Determines how this attribute\'s values are displayed.'=>'決定屬性的值顯示的方式。','This product has produced sales and may be linked to existing orders. Are you sure you want to delete it?'=>'這項產品已製造銷售，且可能已連結現有的訂單。是否確定要刪除？','Read more about &ldquo;%s&rdquo;'=>'深入瞭解「%s」','Cantemir'=>'Cantemir','Cahul'=>'Cahul','Briceni'=>'Briceni','Basarabeasc