ibility with WooCommerce %s yet and should be updated and examined further before you proceed:'=>'下列作用中外掛程式尚未宣告與 WooCommerce %s 相容，繼續執行前應先更新並進一步檢查。','Tested up to WooCommerce version'=>'測試至 WooCommerce 版本','Plugin'=>'外掛程式','unknown'=>'不明','This option will delete ALL of your tax rates, use with caution. This action cannot be reversed.'=>'此選項會刪除你所有的稅率，請小心使用。此動作無法復原。','Delete tax rates'=>'刪除稅率','Create default WooCommerce pages'=>'建立預設 WooCommerce 頁面','Clear customer sessions'=>'清除客戶工作階段','WooCommerce transients'=>'WooCommerce 暫存值','Page settingTerms and conditions'=>'服務條款','<strong>Heads up!</strong> The versions of the following plugins you\'re running haven\'t been tested with WooCommerce %s. Please update them or confirm compatibility before updating WooCommerce, or you may experience issues:'=>'<strong>注意！</strong>下列執行中外掛程式的版本尚未與 WooCommerce %s 進行測試。更新 WooCommerce 前，請先加以更新或確認相容性，否則可能發生問題:','Upload a new file'=>'上傳新檔案','The file is empty or using a different encoding than UTF-8, please try again with a new file.'=>'檔案是空的，或使用與 UTF-8 不同的編碼，請使用新檔案再次嘗試。','Refund #%1$s - %2$s by %3$s'=>'退款 #%1$s - 由 %3$s 於 %2$s 執行','Add shipping'=>'新增運費','The stock has not been updated because the value has changed since editing. Product %1$d has %2$d units in stock.'=>'開始編輯後值已變更，故庫存尚未更新。產品 %1$d 的存貨量為 %2$d 件。','Order details manually sent to customer.'=>'訂單詳細資料已手動傳送給客戶。','Choose an action...'=>'選擇動作...','Position'=>'位置','Lifetime Subscription'=>'終生訂閱','Sort by:'=>'排序:','Send order details to customer'=>'將訂單詳細資料傳送給顧客','Below is a list of extensions available on your WooCommerce.com account. To receive extension updates please make sure the extension is installed, and its subscription activated and connected to your WooCommerce.com account. Extensions can be activated from the <a href="%s">Plugins</a> screen.'=>'以下是你的 WooCommerce.com 帳號上的可用擴充功能清單。 若要收到擴充功能更新，請確保已安裝擴充功能、啟用其訂閱並連結至你的 WooCommerce.com 帳號。 可從「<a href="%s">外掛程式</a>」畫面啟用擴充功能。','Transfer existing products to your new store — just import a CSV file.'=>'將現有產品轉移至你的新商店 — 只需匯入 CSV 檔案即可。','Expired'=>'已到期','Expiring Soon'=>'即將到期','Update Available'=>'有可用更新','If you like %1$s please leave us a %2$s rating. A huge thanks in advance!'=>'如果 %1$s 對網站確有幫助，請給我們 %2$s 評價。開發團隊在此先行致謝。','Have an existing store?'=>'有現有商店嗎？','Import products'=>'匯入商品','Create a product'=>'建立商品','Yes please!'=>'是的，麻煩你！','We\'re here for you — get tips, product updates, and inspiration straight to your mailbox.'=>'我們隨時在這裡為你服務 — 我們會將各項提示、產品更新以及靈感直接寄送到你的信箱。','You\'re ready to start selling!'=>'你已準備好開始販售！','Your site might be on a private network. Jetpack can only connect to public sites. Please make sure your site is visible over the internet, and then try connecting again 🙏.'=>'你的網站可能位於私人網路上。Jetpack 只能連結至公開網站。請確定可透過網際網路看見你的網站，然後再次嘗試連結🙏。','Sorry! We couldn\'t contact Jetpack just now 😭. Please make sure that your site is visible over the internet, and that it accepts incoming and outgoing requests via curl. You can also try to connect to Jetpack again, and if you run into any more issues, please contact support.'=>'很抱歉！我們現在無法連結 Jetpack 😭。請確定可透過網際網路看見你的網站，且網站可透過 curl 接受傳入和傳出要求。你也可以嘗試重新連結至 Jetpack，如果遇到更多問題，請聯絡支援團隊。','Sorry! We tried, but we couldn\'t install Jetpack for you 😭. Please go to the Plugins tab to install it, and finish setting up your store.'=>'很抱歉！我們已經試過了，但無法為你安裝 Jetpack 😭。請前往「外掛程式」標籤以進行安裝，並完成商店設定。','Sorry! We tried, but we couldn\'t connect Jetpack just now 😭. Please go to the Plugins tab to connect Jetpack, so that you can finish setting up your store.'=>'很抱歉！我們已經試過了，但現在無法連結 Jetpack 😭。請前往「外掛程式」標籤以連結 Jetpack，以便完成商店設定。','Share new items on social media the moment they\'re live in your store.'=>'在社群媒體上分享你商店中的新項目。','Product promotion'=>'商品促銷','Get an alert if your store is down for even a few minutes.'=>'如果你的商店僅停止運作幾分鐘，也會收到警示。','Store monitoring'=>'商店監控','Get insights on how your store is doing, including total sales, top products, and more.'=>'深入剖析商店如何運作，包含銷售總計、熱門產品等內容。','Finish setting up your store'=>'完成商店設定','Store sta